WEBVTT

00:00:38.791 --> 00:00:40.625
Ni vigumu kujua wapi pa kuanzia.

00:00:41.833 --> 00:00:45.250
Nadhani nisimulie hadithi ya mauaji ya Ijumaa Kuu kupitia macho yangu,

00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:46.958
Lazima nianzie hapa.

00:00:47.625 --> 00:00:51.750
Miezi tisa iliyopita, wakati shemasi huyu mkorofi aliposema kitu kisicho cha kawaida,

00:00:51.833 --> 00:00:53.041
na nilifanya hivi.

00:00:58.333 --> 00:00:59.958
Loo, jamani.

00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:03.083
Kwa hivyo, wewe ni mpiganaji, basi?

00:01:03.583 --> 00:01:05.708
Uh, hapana, Baba, sivyo kabisa.

00:01:05.791 --> 00:01:09.041
Naam, tuna shemasi ambaye angesema vinginevyo kama taya yake isingevunjika.

00:01:09.125 --> 00:01:11.750
Katika maisha yangu ya awali, ndio, nilikuwa bondia,

00:01:12.250 --> 00:01:14.833
na niliishi mitaani. Nilifanya mambo mengine.

00:01:14.916 --> 00:01:18.708
Tunahitaji wapiganaji leo, lakini ili kupigana na ulimwengu,

00:01:19.458 --> 00:01:21.083
si sisi wenyewe.

00:01:21.166 --> 00:01:24.625
Kuhani ni mchungaji. Dunia ni mbwa mwitu.

00:01:24.708 --> 00:01:25.833
Hapana.

00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:33.625
Mimi… Siamini hivyo, Baba, kwa heshima.

00:01:33.708 --> 00:01:36.500
Unaanza kupigana na mbwa mwitu, na kabla hujajua,

00:01:36.583 --> 00:01:38.291
Kila mtu ambaye humjui ni mbwa mwitu.

00:01:39.333 --> 00:01:42.333
Bado nina silika hiyo ya kupigana, na nimekubali leo,

00:01:42.416 --> 00:01:44.833
lakini Kristo alikuja kuponya ulimwengu, si kuupigania.

00:01:44.916 --> 00:01:46.208
Ninaamini hivyo.

00:01:46.291 --> 00:01:49.583
Ni hii, si hii, unajua?

00:01:50.833 --> 00:01:52.666
Nataka tu kuwa kuhani mzuri.

00:01:53.625 --> 00:01:56.916
Waonyeshe watu waliovunjika moyo kama mimi msamaha na upendo wa Kristo.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:59.000
Dunia inamhitaji sana.

00:02:01.708 --> 00:02:04.583
Nipe jaribio moja zaidi, na ninaahidi nitafanya hivyo.

00:02:16.958 --> 00:02:18.125
Mheshimiwa,

00:02:18.833 --> 00:02:21.041
Umeninyooshea shingo mara nyingi sana.

00:02:21.125 --> 00:02:23.625
-Nimekukatisha tamaa, na chochote kile -- -Sawa.

00:02:23.708 --> 00:02:24.791
Sikiliza…

00:02:25.291 --> 00:02:28.250
Deacon Clark ni maarufu kwa uume wake.

00:02:28.333 --> 00:02:30.791
Hakuna mtu aliyekasirika sana kwamba umemtazama kwa saa.

00:02:30.875 --> 00:02:32.375
Kwa kweli, kinyume chake.

00:02:32.458 --> 00:02:35.041
Lakini tunahitaji kufanya jambo fulani kuihusu.

00:02:36.041 --> 00:02:39.250
Tunakutuma kwenye parokia ndogo huko Chimney Rock.

00:02:39.333 --> 00:02:42.375
Ni kasisi mmoja tu hapo sasa.

00:02:43.666 --> 00:02:45.000
Mchungaji msaidizi?

00:02:45.083 --> 00:02:47.250
Naam, punguza shauku yako.

00:02:47.333 --> 00:02:48.166
Nini?

00:02:48.666 --> 00:02:53.416
Unaenda kwa Mama Yetu wa Ushujaa wa Milele,

00:02:53.500 --> 00:02:56.583
ikiongozwa na Monsignor Jefferson Wicks. Je, umewahi kusikia kuhusu Jefferson Wicks?

00:02:57.458 --> 00:03:00.958
Sawa, tazama, Wicks ana wafuasi wake hapa. Mimi si mmoja wao.

00:03:01.041 --> 00:03:02.125
Kati yako na mimi,

00:03:02.208 --> 00:03:05.166
Nadhani ana pembe chache tu za rozari kamili na mwana halisi wa mbwa mwitu.

00:03:06.166 --> 00:03:10.833
Lakini jambo lisilopingika ni kwamba kundi lake linapungua na hata kuzidi kuwa na uzito.

00:03:11.791 --> 00:03:15.333
Inaweza kutumia baadhi ya yale uliyosema humo ndani. Unaelewa?

00:03:15.958 --> 00:03:18.291
Sio kabisa, lakini ndiyo.

00:03:18.375 --> 00:03:20.458
Ndiyo, ndiyo, ndiyo, ndiyo, ndiyo.

00:03:20.541 --> 00:03:23.416
-Roho amenishika. Acha nimkabili. -Hei. Hei, hei.

00:03:23.500 --> 00:03:27.041
Hii, si hii, sivyo? Mm?

00:03:31.166 --> 00:03:32.375
Bahati nzuri, kijana.

00:03:38.166 --> 00:03:40.791
Kwa hivyo, ndivyo nilivyofika Chimney Rock.

00:03:43.333 --> 00:03:45.166
Danieli katika tundu la simba.

00:03:45.250 --> 00:03:47.000
Daudi akimkabili Goliathi.

00:03:47.500 --> 00:03:49.916
Vijana, bubu, na waliojaa Kristo.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.750
Tayari kwa chochote.

00:04:23.791 --> 00:04:24.875
Baba Jefferson?

00:04:25.791 --> 00:04:28.083
Habari. Jud Duplenticy kutoka Albany?

00:04:28.166 --> 00:04:30.875
Bwana awe nawe, Jud Duplenticy kutoka Albany.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.125
Umekuja hapa kuniondolea kanisa langu?

00:04:37.458 --> 00:04:39.250
Loo. Hapana.

00:04:39.833 --> 00:04:40.708
Nzuri.

00:04:41.583 --> 00:04:44.000
Sawa, niite Monsignor Wicks.

00:04:44.916 --> 00:04:46.208
Naona umekutana na Martha.

00:04:47.083 --> 00:04:48.333
Martha? Hapana.

00:04:48.416 --> 00:04:49.916
-Monsignor Wicks. -Yesu!

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:52.500
Niliamka mapema ili kung'arisha fedha.

00:04:52.583 --> 00:04:53.875
Ilikuwa na madoa kidogo.

00:04:53.958 --> 00:04:55.500
Hiyo itakuwa sawa, Martha.

00:04:55.583 --> 00:04:57.791
Baba… Yuda.

00:04:59.083 --> 00:05:00.375
Karibu hapa.

00:05:00.875 --> 00:05:02.500
-Asante, Martha. -Mm.

00:05:02.583 --> 00:05:05.208
Kwa kweli nilikuwa nikimwambia tu Baba Wicks…

00:05:05.291 --> 00:05:06.875
Monsignor Wicks.

00:05:07.708 --> 00:05:09.583
Monsignor, sawa. Samahani.

00:05:10.083 --> 00:05:11.708
Na samahani kwa kusema "Yesu".

00:05:13.500 --> 00:05:15.666
Hoo. Hii inaendelea vizuri, nadhani.

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:18.291
-Askofu Langstrom alikutuma, sivyo? -Mm-hmm.

00:05:19.166 --> 00:05:20.250
Mkondo mrefu.

00:05:20.750 --> 00:05:22.416
Ninamjua vizuri.

00:05:22.500 --> 00:05:24.708
Alikuchagua mwenyewe, akakutuma hapa.

00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:27.000
Inaniambia kitu.

00:05:29.583 --> 00:05:30.791
Inaniambia mengi.

00:05:31.916 --> 00:05:34.708
Naam, mimi… Najua umezoea kuruka peke yako, lakini, um…

00:05:35.291 --> 00:05:36.916
Mimi niko hapa kuhudumia.

00:05:38.416 --> 00:05:39.625
Chukua ungamo langu.

00:05:41.291 --> 00:05:43.083
Sawa.

00:05:43.791 --> 00:05:45.083
Mm.

00:05:47.166 --> 00:05:49.708
Nibariki, Baba, kwa kuwa nimetenda dhambi.

00:05:49.791 --> 00:05:51.000
Imekuwa, uh,

00:05:51.875 --> 00:05:54.291
wiki sita tangu nilipokiri mara ya mwisho.

00:05:58.708 --> 00:06:01.250
Nimewaonea wivu utajiri wa wengine.

00:06:02.125 --> 00:06:06.750
Niliona tangazo hili la magari ya kifahari. Sam alikuwa nalo kwenye TV yake. Lexus.

00:06:07.416 --> 00:06:08.625
Nami nikawaza,

00:06:09.125 --> 00:06:11.875
"Ah! Hilo ni gari zuri."

00:06:11.958 --> 00:06:13.458
Coupe.

00:06:14.583 --> 00:06:17.958
Uh… Nimewaonea wivu watu mashuhuri.

00:06:19.375 --> 00:06:22.750
Nilihusudu mamlaka ya babu yangu kama kasisi. Nilitaka hilo.

00:06:22.833 --> 00:06:24.041
Daima alifanya hivyo.

00:06:25.791 --> 00:06:26.791
Uh…

00:06:27.541 --> 00:06:28.958
Nimejichua,

00:06:30.166 --> 00:06:33.708
um, mara nne wiki hii.

00:06:33.791 --> 00:06:36.625
Nne au tano, kwa ujumla, katika… Nilisema nini, wiki sita?

00:06:36.708 --> 00:06:39.791
Tuseme mara 30, amejichua.

00:06:40.833 --> 00:06:44.458
Uh, wiki hii, kitandani mwangu, asubuhi mara moja.

00:06:44.958 --> 00:06:49.041
Mara tu nilipokuwa nimeoga, nikisimama, jambo ambalo lilikuwa rahisi.

00:06:49.125 --> 00:06:51.250
Tumia jeli ya kuogea tu.

00:06:52.333 --> 00:06:55.541
Loo, mara moja katikati ya usiku, baada ya ndoto kuhusu--

00:06:55.625 --> 00:06:58.208
-Hiyo ni sawa. -Kuhusu moja ya mikahawa ya paka ya Kijapani.

00:06:58.291 --> 00:07:00.625
-Sawa. -Unajua, nilisoma makala hii,

00:07:00.708 --> 00:07:05.916
lakini paka walikuwa wasichana, na, unajua, kwa hivyo…

00:07:06.583 --> 00:07:08.000
Na sikuwa nimejiandaa,

00:07:08.083 --> 00:07:12.125
kwa hivyo ilinibidi nimalizie nakala ya jarida la Catholic Chronicle,

00:07:12.833 --> 00:07:16.916
kile tu kilichokuwa mezani, ambacho labda ni aina yake ya dhambi.

00:07:17.416 --> 00:07:20.416
Sijui, labda sivyo, lakini… Sio nzuri.

00:07:21.541 --> 00:07:23.833
Wakati huo, nilidhani hii ilikuwa ya ajabu tu.

00:07:24.833 --> 00:07:26.916
Lakini nikiangalia nyuma sasa, najua.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:29.333
Huu ulikuwa ngumi ya kwanza ya Wicks.

00:07:29.416 --> 00:07:31.458
Salamu Maria Tano na Utukufu Mmoja.

00:07:33.166 --> 00:07:34.458
Asante, Baba.

00:07:40.041 --> 00:07:41.541
Haingekuwa ya mwisho kwake.

00:07:41.625 --> 00:07:42.875
Loo, na karibu

00:07:43.666 --> 00:07:45.083
kanisani kwangu.

00:07:48.750 --> 00:07:51.208
Katika wiki chache zilizofuata, nilizoea

00:07:51.291 --> 00:07:53.500
katika Mama Yetu wa Ushujaa wa Daima.

00:07:59.166 --> 00:08:03.791
Mfanyakazi mwingine pekee wa muda wote alikuwa mtunza bustani, Samson.

00:08:04.500 --> 00:08:05.583
Peke yangu.

00:08:11.125 --> 00:08:12.833
Ni Monsignor Wicks

00:08:12.916 --> 00:08:17.000
ambaye hunipa nguvu kila siku ili nisirudi kwenye chupa.

00:08:17.916 --> 00:08:19.041
Alikuwa akinywa pia.

00:08:20.125 --> 00:08:24.083
Lakini aliniambia mara moja, "Kama naweza kumzuia pepo huyo, unaweza."

00:08:25.375 --> 00:08:27.291
Na kila siku, ni mapambano.

00:08:28.166 --> 00:08:29.250
Lakini nimewahi.

00:08:30.541 --> 00:08:34.041
Ninamsifu yeye na… Martha wangu mpendwa.

00:08:34.125 --> 00:08:36.625
Martha wako mtamu?

00:08:36.708 --> 00:08:38.333
Ningemfanyia chochote.

00:08:39.708 --> 00:08:42.083
Malaika wangu Duniani.

00:08:42.166 --> 00:08:45.458
Kuhusu kanisa, Martha ndiye anayefanya yote.

00:08:45.541 --> 00:08:48.750
Anahifadhi vitabu, anasimamia michango, anawasilisha kila kitu.

00:08:48.833 --> 00:08:49.958
Faili hiyo.

00:08:50.541 --> 00:08:52.958
Anafua nguo, anahifadhi vifaa,

00:08:53.041 --> 00:08:55.166
hulisha Wicks, hucheza kinanda.

00:08:58.875 --> 00:09:00.791
Alijua mahali ambapo miili hiyo ilizikwa.

00:09:01.583 --> 00:09:03.666
-Kwa hivyo hii ndiyo siri? -Ndiyo.

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:06.708
Ni aibu kubwa. Lazima niweke kamera ya usalama.

00:09:07.208 --> 00:09:09.333
-Je, kuna mlango wa kuingilia? -Kuna mlango.

00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:11.708
Hii hapa hapa,

00:09:12.208 --> 00:09:13.333
Ni mlango wa Lazaro.

00:09:14.041 --> 00:09:16.916
Huchukua vifaa vya ujenzi kufungua kutoka nje.

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.875
Lakini imeshindwa kufanya hivyo ili kushinikiza moja

00:09:20.458 --> 00:09:22.875
itaitupa chini kutoka ndani.

00:09:24.125 --> 00:09:25.458
Ni nani basi aliye ndani?

00:09:25.541 --> 00:09:26.541
Prentice.

00:09:27.166 --> 00:09:30.625
Babu yake Wicks, mwanzilishi wa kanisa hili.

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:33.000
Alikuwa kama baba kwangu.

00:09:33.666 --> 00:09:35.666
Inanifanya niwe mgonjwa.

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:40.000
Watoto hawa wakichora meli za roketi kote katika sehemu yake takatifu ya kupumzika.

00:09:46.708 --> 00:09:49.416
-Unafanya nini? -Oh, uh...

00:09:50.208 --> 00:09:52.125
Naam, mimi hufanya kazi kidogo ya mbao,

00:09:52.208 --> 00:09:55.708
kwa hivyo nilifikiri ningeweza kuazima baadhi ya vifaa vya Sam, kutengeneza kifaa sahihi--

00:09:55.791 --> 00:09:57.000
Hapana, tunaacha hilo.

00:09:57.083 --> 00:09:59.958
Ukumbusho wa dhambi ya aibu ya kahaba kahaba.

00:10:01.500 --> 00:10:02.916
Chukua ungamo langu.

00:10:04.875 --> 00:10:06.625
Ndiyo, kahaba.

00:10:08.125 --> 00:10:09.625
Huyo alikuwa mama yake Wicks.

00:10:09.708 --> 00:10:12.333
Sawa, kwa hivyo kuna nini na hilo?

00:10:12.416 --> 00:10:14.625
Alikuwa kahaba na kahaba.

00:10:15.458 --> 00:10:16.291
Sawa.

00:10:16.375 --> 00:10:19.583
Prentice alipoingia katika ukuhani na kuanzisha kanisa hili,

00:10:19.666 --> 00:10:21.833
alikuwa mjane na binti.

00:10:22.958 --> 00:10:24.541
Neema lilikuwa jina lake.

00:10:25.125 --> 00:10:26.750
Daima mbegu mbaya.

00:10:26.833 --> 00:10:32.166
Alipenda nguo zinazoonyesha umbo lake na chapa zake za kifahari.

00:10:32.250 --> 00:10:33.875
Chapa za kifahari… Loo!

00:10:33.958 --> 00:10:35.041
-Mm. -Ndiyo.

00:10:35.125 --> 00:10:37.958
Akiwa kijana, alijivinjari kwenye baa,

00:10:38.041 --> 00:10:40.250
hivi karibuni alikuwa na mimba ya mtoto aliyesafiri kwa maji machafu.

00:10:41.250 --> 00:10:45.291
Prentice alikuwa na utajiri mkubwa wa familia katika benki.

00:10:45.375 --> 00:10:48.416
Ili kumlinda mjukuu wake, Wicks,

00:10:48.500 --> 00:10:53.083
aliahidi kwamba ikiwa Grace angebaki chini ya paa lake,

00:10:53.791 --> 00:10:56.916
bahati hiyo ingemhusu yeye.

00:10:57.916 --> 00:11:01.750
Na hivyo kahaba huyo alimsubiri baba yake afe.

00:11:02.666 --> 00:11:05.083
Loo, ilimlemea sana.

00:11:05.166 --> 00:11:06.666
Martha, kumbuka hili.

00:11:07.833 --> 00:11:10.666
Utajiri na nguvu inayoambatana nao,

00:11:11.416 --> 00:11:12.666
ni Tufaha la Hawa.

00:11:13.916 --> 00:11:16.041
Jaribu linalosababisha kuanguka.

00:11:17.291 --> 00:11:21.125
Lazima niwalinde wapendwa wetu kutokana na ushawishi wake mbaya,

00:11:22.208 --> 00:11:23.625
kwa gharama yoyote.

00:11:24.375 --> 00:11:26.208
Siku yake hatimaye ilifika.

00:11:26.291 --> 00:11:27.541
Nilikuwa pale.

00:11:28.625 --> 00:11:31.833
Nilimwona Prentice akipokea komunio yake ya mwisho

00:11:31.916 --> 00:11:34.666
na kufa juu ya madhabahu takatifu.

00:11:34.750 --> 00:11:36.166
Kwa amani.

00:11:36.958 --> 00:11:40.458
Kahaba huyo alienda moja kwa moja kwa wakili wa Prentice.

00:11:41.041 --> 00:11:44.125
"Nipe pesa zangu," alisema.

00:11:45.375 --> 00:11:46.833
Na unajua alichosema?

00:11:47.958 --> 00:11:52.458
"Ndiyo, wewe ni mrithi wa kila senti Prentice alikuwa nayo."

00:11:53.250 --> 00:11:54.875
Na katika masimulizi yake,

00:11:56.166 --> 00:11:59.166
hakuna hata senti moja ya moto.

00:11:59.875 --> 00:12:02.041
Mm, alifanya nini na utajiri huo?

00:12:02.125 --> 00:12:04.041
Niliwapa maskini, tuseme baadhi.

00:12:04.666 --> 00:12:07.541
Waliitupa baharini, wanasema wengine. Hakuna anayejua.

00:12:08.416 --> 00:12:09.416
Ilikuwa imetoweka.

00:12:10.375 --> 00:12:14.208
Tendo la mwisho la neema la mtu huyo mtakatifu

00:12:15.333 --> 00:12:19.625
ilikuwa ni kuizuia uovu unaoharibu kutoka kwa mikono ya waovu.

00:12:20.666 --> 00:12:22.500
Yote aliyomwachia…

00:12:25.541 --> 00:12:26.541
ilikuwa hivi.

00:12:27.166 --> 00:12:29.208
"Hiki ni nini?" alisema.

00:12:30.291 --> 00:12:31.708
Lakini nilijua.

00:12:32.416 --> 00:12:34.250
Usitafute tufaha la Hawa.

00:12:34.916 --> 00:12:38.333
Urithi wako sasa ni Kristo.

00:12:44.208 --> 00:12:46.833
Usiku huo, alilipiza kisasi.

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:52.000
Katika hasira ya kishetani,

00:12:52.083 --> 00:12:56.166
alichafua mahali hapa patakatifu.

00:13:11.416 --> 00:13:13.833
Kukufuru, unajisi.

00:13:15.416 --> 00:13:18.416
Uovu uliojifanya kuwa mwili.

00:13:54.083 --> 00:13:56.458
Nikasema, "Dada Grace,

00:13:56.541 --> 00:14:01.458
Mungu, Baba yenu, atawasamehe kwa upendo wake."

00:14:18.041 --> 00:14:19.541
Alikufa,

00:14:20.083 --> 00:14:22.375
akijitupa kwenye kaburi la Prentice.

00:14:25.541 --> 00:14:27.541
Walisema aneurysm ya ubongo.

00:14:28.750 --> 00:14:30.666
Nimepigwa chini, nasema,

00:14:31.541 --> 00:14:34.875
na Mungu katika rehema zake.

00:14:35.958 --> 00:14:37.500
Shit takatifu.

00:14:39.666 --> 00:14:40.666
Samahani, samahani.

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:46.333
Giza la hadithi hiyo lilikuwa msingi wa mahali hapa.

00:14:46.416 --> 00:14:48.666
Ungeweza kuhisi.

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:50.083
Akauliza, "Nani alikuambia ..."

00:14:50.166 --> 00:14:54.500
Kwa hivyo ni nini kingemvutia mtu kuifanya hii kuwa nyumba yake ya kiroho?

00:14:55.083 --> 00:14:58.083
Kundi kuu la wahudumu wa kawaida wote walikuwa na sababu zao.

00:14:58.166 --> 00:15:00.125
Na hawa watakuwa washukiwa wetu.

00:15:00.208 --> 00:15:01.833
Kwa hivyo ninapaswa kuwatambulisha.

00:15:02.500 --> 00:15:06.208
Vera Draven, wakili wa eneo hilo. Alikuwa mwaminifu na mcha Mungu.

00:15:08.625 --> 00:15:11.958
Baba yangu alikuwa wakili wa Wicks na rafiki wa unywaji pombe.

00:15:12.041 --> 00:15:14.166
Wavulana.

00:15:14.250 --> 00:15:18.625
Na kwa hivyo ukawa wakili ili uweze kuchukua jukumu la familia yake?

00:15:18.708 --> 00:15:21.791
Nikawa mwanasheria kwa sababu nilitaka kufanya mambo makubwa duniani.

00:15:23.125 --> 00:15:25.958
Lakini mahali hapa ni urithi wa baba yangu.

00:15:26.708 --> 00:15:27.750
