00:19:25.333 --> 00:19:28.000
Hatumpendi. Sote tunasema, "Wicks. Kuwa mwangalifu,

00:19:28.083 --> 00:19:32.166
Lazima umtie moyo. Ni habari mbaya. Mshairi mwenye bahati.

