Unawauliza hata wale walio wagumu zaidi kwenye viti,

00:22:35.458 --> 00:22:38.125
watasema, hapana, bila shaka hii sivyo wanavyoamini.

00:22:38.208 --> 00:22:40.958
Ni Wicks akiwa Wicks, akiisukuma mbali sana.

00:22:41.041 --> 00:22:44.958
Na anachokisukuma kila wakati ni kuondoka.

00:22:46.458 --> 00:22:47.875
Kwa nini anafanya hivi?

