00:25:18.750 --> 00:25:21.166
-Anasema, "Kitu gani?" -Oh.

00:25:21.250 --> 00:25:23.458
-Jeez. -Nina… samahani. Baba,

00:25:23.541 --> 00:25:27.541
Nilikuja kwa sababu nilidhani hii ilikuwa sherehe rasmi ya kanisa.

00:25:27.625 --> 00:25:29.833
Ila yeye hakutumia neno "heck".

00:25:29.916 --> 00:25:31.458
Sawa, asante, Martha.

00:25:31.541 --> 00:25:32.875
Hii ni ibada ya kanisa, Vera.

00:25:32.958 --> 00:25:34.791
