00:26:20.833 --> 00:26:23.250
Ndiyo, ningeweza.

00:26:23.333 --> 00:26:24.416
Naam,

00:26:25.625 --> 00:26:27.041
vizuri!

00:26:59.583 --> 00:27:03.416
Wiki Takatifu, wiki ya ibada maalum zinazoelekea Pasaka.

00:27:04.375 --> 00:27:07.208
Ilikuwa Jumapili ya Matawi ndipo hatimaye niliposhindwa.

00:27:07.291 --> 00:27:10.500
