00:27:11.333 --> 00:27:14.791
kufanya jambo lile nililokuambia kuhusu mahali ninaposhikilia mkono wangu chini juu?

00:27:16.041 --> 00:27:18.458
Baba zetu watano, Salamu Maria watano.

00:27:19.791 --> 00:27:22.250
Naam, tuko katika miezi tisa sasa, Jud.

00:27:23.791 --> 00:27:28.583
Unafurahiaje hapa? Unabomoa baadhi ya kuta?

00:27:32.250 --> 00:27:36.125
