00:27:40.208 --> 00:27:42.833
Nilisaliti faragha ya kasisi mwenzangu.

00:27:44.041 --> 00:27:47.458
Ninajua kwamba Martha huhifadhi bili zake za matibabu ofisini, kwa hivyo…

00:27:48.416 --> 00:27:49.625
Nilipitia hayo.

00:27:50.666 --> 00:27:53.375
Na niligundua kuwa ulifanyiwa upasuaji wa kuondoa tezi dume miaka mitano iliyopita,

00:27:53.458 --> 00:27:56.708
kukufanya ushindwe kimwili kusimama.

00:27:59.166 --> 00:28:01.583
Naweza kushughulikia chochote hiki.

00:28:02.125 --> 00:28:05.708
Kwa miezi tisa iliyopita, nimeona jinsi unavyowatunza kundi hili,

00:28:05.791 --> 00:28:07.125
na sipendi.

00:28:07.208 --> 00:28:08.291
Hupendi?

00:28:08.375 --> 00:28:10.208
Hapana, Monsignor, sijui.

00:28:10.291 --> 00:28:11.500
Nat Sharp.

00:28:11.583 --> 00:28:14.791
Mwanadamu anahitaji kusamehe na kuanza kuishi maisha yake.

00:28:14.875 --> 00:28:17.791
Na upendo wa Kristo unapaswa kuwa njia ya kuanzia kwa hilo, na badala yake,

00:28:17.875 --> 00:28:19.583
Yeye ni mtu wa haki, kila siku,

00:28:19.666 --> 00:28:22.875
akizidi kuwa na hasira na uchungu dhidi ya mke wake wa zamani,

00:28:22.958 --> 00:28:23.958
dhidi ya wanawake.

00:28:24.916 --> 00:28:28.250
Ni mbaya. Na Lee, yeye ni msimuliaji wa hadithi.

00:28:28.333 --> 00:28:31.833
Na ni kama nguvu zake kuu zimegeuzwa dhidi yake.

00:28:31.916 --> 00:28:34.791
Hadithi pekee anayosimulia ni, "Dunia inataka kuniua."

00:28:34.875 --> 00:28:38.125
Alikuwa mcheshi mzuri, mwerevu na mwenye heshima,

00:28:38.208 --> 00:28:43.791
na sasa anazunguka-zunguka na kukasirika kila wakati, akiwa na wasiwasi.

00:28:43.875 --> 00:28:46.916
Je, unajua kwamba alijenga handaki kuzunguka nyumba yake?

00:28:47.500 --> 00:28:48.333
Kweli?

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:52.333
Namaanisha, kwa kiasi kikubwa ni ishara, lakini ndio.

00:28:53.125 --> 00:28:55.125
Na Simone, samahani, Monsignor,

00:28:55.208 --> 00:28:57.416
lakini ninaogopa umemtumia vibaya.

00:28:57.500 --> 00:28:59.333
Nimeona nambari za michango.

00:29:00.000 --> 00:29:02.125
Najua ni kiasi gani anatoa, na miezi michache iliyopita,

00:29:02.208 --> 00:29:03.916
kimsingi anaunga mkono mahali hapa.

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:07.708
Na ndiyo, naamini katika uwezekano wa miujiza kupitia Kristo,

00:29:07.791 --> 00:29:09.791
lakini unachompa si hivyo.

00:29:11.000 --> 00:29:13.208
Ni shughuli za kibiashara, kupitia wewe,

00:29:13.291 --> 00:29:15.625
na Mungu akusaidie, inamfanya ahisi amesalitiwa tena.

00:29:16.208 --> 00:29:17.875
Mungu anisaidie. Kuna kingine chochote?

00:29:17.958 --> 00:29:20.208
Ndiyo, kwa nini isiwe hivyo? Cy Draven.

00:29:20.291 --> 00:29:23.666
Je, mambo haya mapya ya YouTube anayofanya hayakusumbui?

00:29:23.750 --> 00:29:26.166
Kila wiki sasa, anapiga vipande kutoka kwa unachosema katika Misa

00:29:26.250 --> 00:29:30.750
na kuziingiza katika kauli zake za kisiasa. Anaunga mkono, na kwa uaminifu,

00:29:30.833 --> 00:29:33.416
Nadhani kuipotosha kanisa kwa njia hatari.

00:29:34.666 --> 00:29:38.333
Ni lini mara ya mwisho mtu mpya alidumu zaidi ya Jumapili moja?

00:29:38.958 --> 00:29:40.333
Neno limetoka.

00:29:40.916 --> 00:29:42.916
Kila wiki sasa, ni hivi tu…

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:45.000
uvimbe huu mgumu wa kawaida,

00:29:45.083 --> 00:29:49.375
na inaonekana kama unawaweka kwa makusudi hasira na woga.

00:29:50.333 --> 00:29:52.041
Je, hivyo ndivyo Kristo alivyoongoza kundi lake?

00:29:52.125 --> 00:29:54.250
Je, hivyo ndivyo tunavyopaswa kufanya?

00:30:02.791 --> 00:30:06.458
Kwa sasa, umekasirika. Unapaswa kuwa na hasira.

00:30:06.541 --> 00:30:08.875
Ingekuwa hatari kama usingekuwa. Ningeona huna msaada,

00:30:08.958 --> 00:30:11.000
na ningefanya hivyo tena na tena.

00:30:11.791 --> 00:30:14.166
Mimi ni ulimwengu. Wewe ndiye kanisa.

00:30:14.250 --> 00:30:17.125
Kaa hapo. Kaa hapo. Kaa hapo.

00:30:18.500 --> 00:30:21.958
Aha. Nzuri. Sawa. Ndiyo.

00:30:22.541 --> 00:30:26.625
Hasira. Hasira huturuhusu kupigana, kurudisha ardhi tuliyopoteza.

00:30:27.208 --> 00:30:29.375
Na tumepoteza nafasi nyingi sana.

00:30:29.958 --> 00:30:31.083
Na sasa unaogopa.

00:30:31.166 --> 00:30:34.041
Tazama silika hizo za mikono mitupu zikirudi. Vizuri!

00:30:34.875 --> 00:30:37.333
Unaogopa nitakuja tena kwako.

00:30:37.416 --> 00:30:40.750
Lakini unajilinda.

00:30:43.125 --> 00:30:46.541
Kwa sababu dunia inataka kutuangamiza.

00:30:47.500 --> 00:30:51.333
Toleo lako la upendo na msamaha ni kama tone.

00:30:51.416 --> 00:30:54.416
Inaendelea kuendana na usasa,

00:30:54.500 --> 00:30:56.708
kutotaka kuudhi ulimwengu huu wa takataka.

00:30:56.791 --> 00:31:00.041
Wakati huo huo, wanatuangamiza.

00:31:00.708 --> 00:31:05.125
Makahaba wa Marxist wa kike. Kidogo kidogo, wanafanya hivyo.

00:31:07.208 --> 00:31:10.416
Lakini mimi hubeba mzigo wangu. Ninashikilia mstari.

00:31:12.458 --> 00:31:13.541
Na wewe?

00:31:14.750 --> 00:31:17.166
Wewe ni mtoto wa kawaida kutoka Albany?

00:31:19.666 --> 00:31:21.291
Je, utakasirika?

00:31:22.375 --> 00:31:23.750
na kupigana?

00:31:32.083 --> 00:31:34.083
Unatia sumu kanisa hili.

00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:37.666
Nami nitafanya chochote kinachohitajika ili kuiokoa.

00:31:39.458 --> 00:31:41.291
Ili kukukatiza kama saratani.

00:31:44.500 --> 00:31:46.916
Baba zetu watano, Salamu Maria watano.

00:32:07.583 --> 00:32:09.583
Kristo, hukuniacha.

00:32:10.166 --> 00:32:12.416
Sikati tamaa na kanisa hili.

00:32:14.916 --> 00:32:16.833
Lakini alikuwa hatua moja mbele yangu.

00:32:17.666 --> 00:32:20.083
Mkutano wa maombi wa Baba Jud?

00:32:20.791 --> 00:32:22.291
Nimehifadhi kanisa hili.

00:32:22.375 --> 00:32:24.083
Nimeiimarisha kwa ukweli wa Mungu.

00:32:24.166 --> 00:32:27.458
Na sasa usaliti wa kupata mamlaka yangu

00:32:27.541 --> 00:32:30.666
na imani na maisha yenyewe yanapingwa,

00:32:30.750 --> 00:32:32.833
na kutoka ndani ya patakatifu pangu mwenyewe.

00:32:35.333 --> 00:32:36.416
Toka nje!

00:32:40.166 --> 00:32:41.791
Hatua ya mwisho ya Wicks.

00:32:41.875 --> 00:32:43.708
Vita vya wazi dhidi yangu.

00:32:46.500 --> 00:32:48.166
Nilipata ladha nzuri sana.

00:32:48.750 --> 00:32:51.583
Dunia ni mbwa mwitu. Wewe shetani.

00:32:51.666 --> 00:32:53.291
Wewe mbwa mwitu shetani.

00:32:53.791 --> 00:32:55.208
Wewe ni mbwa mwitu shetani.

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:57.208
Shit.

00:32:57.708 --> 00:33:01.250
-Loo! Nikolai, samahani. Nilivunja hilo… -Hapana, hapana, hapana. Usijali kuhusu hilo.

00:33:01.333 --> 00:33:03.750
-…kwa mkono wangu. -Ni taa za takataka. Ni taa za takataka.

00:33:03.833 --> 00:33:05.583
-Njoo. Haya, unafaa kuendesha gari? -Ndiyo.

00:33:05.666 --> 00:33:06.500
Una uhakika?

00:33:22.708 --> 00:33:23.833
Habari!

00:33:26.625 --> 00:33:27.833
Nani yuko hapo?

00:33:27.916 --> 00:33:28.875
Loo, jamani.

00:33:30.333 --> 00:33:32.458
Na hilo linatuleta kwenye Ijumaa Kuu.

00:33:34.625 --> 00:33:36.000
Haya tuendelee.

00:33:36.083 --> 00:33:38.208
Ilikuwa ibada ya saa 3:00 usiku.

00:33:39.125 --> 00:33:40.375
Wahudumu wa kawaida tu.

00:33:41.208 --> 00:33:43.000
Kulikuwa na mvutano wa ajabu hewani.

00:33:43.708 --> 00:33:46.000
Sikumbuki mahubiri, lakini yalihisi tofauti.

00:33:47.500 --> 00:33:49.875
Hasira ilihisi kutokuwa na mawazo mengi.

00:33:50.875 --> 00:33:51.791
Isiyo na mkazo zaidi.

00:33:57.708 --> 00:34:01.375
Kama kawaida, baada ya mahubiri, Wicks alimaliza,

00:34:01.458 --> 00:34:04.666
kihisia na kimwili, na alihitaji muda wa kupona.

00:34:06.708 --> 00:34:09.041
Angejificha kwenye kabati dogo la kuhifadhia vitu

00:34:09.125 --> 00:34:12.000
upande wa patakatifu ili asionekane.

00:34:13.208 --> 00:34:16.291
Angejiimarisha, nami ningeendelea na huduma

00:34:16.375 --> 00:34:19.541
hadi alipohisi nguvu ya kutosha kujiunga tena na kuchukua nafasi.

00:34:19.625 --> 00:34:22.458
Tazama mbao za msalaba

00:34:22.541 --> 00:34:25.625
Ambapo wokovu wa ulimwengu ulining'inia

00:34:34.458 --> 00:34:35.708
Monsignor?

00:34:50.166 --> 00:34:51.250
Kuna nini?

00:34:53.083 --> 00:34:54.125
Jefferson?

00:35:16.583 --> 00:35:17.500
Yuda.

00:35:20.625 --> 00:35:21.833
Kuna kitu mgongoni mwake.

00:35:22.416 --> 00:35:23.583
Subiri. Usiguse.

00:35:24.500 --> 00:35:25.916
Usiguse chochote.

00:35:44.458 --> 00:35:46.583
Shetani! Shetani alimpiga chini!

00:35:46.666 --> 00:35:48.166
-Ibilisi… Shetani… -Martha.

00:35:48.250 --> 00:35:49.833
-...alimpiga chini! -Lo, hapana.

00:35:49.916 --> 00:35:52.708
Martha! Tafadhali.

00:36:29.500 --> 00:36:32.083
Ambulensi ilichukua dakika tano tu kufika.

00:36:34.458 --> 00:36:36.583
Wicks alitangazwa kuwa amekufa papo hapo.

00:36:37.291 --> 00:36:40.916
Nilipojiunga na wengine nje, polisi walikuwa wanawasili tu.

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.833
Ibilisi hatamchukua mtu huyo.

00:36:43.916 --> 00:36:46.750
Atafufuka tena katika utukufu wa Bwana.

00:36:47.750 --> 00:36:50.583
Hili lilikuwa tukio la ajabu kwa mji mdogo,

00:36:50.666 --> 00:36:54.666
na maskini Geraldine, chifu wa eneo hilo, alitupwa chini kwa kichwa.

00:36:54.750 --> 00:36:56.166
Kristo.

00:36:57.375 --> 00:37:00.583
Saa za kuhoji siku nzima Jumamosi

00:37:01.250 --> 00:37:03.958
-mpaka hatimaye… -Wewe ndiye pekee jukwaani

00:37:04.041 --> 00:37:06.291
pamoja na Monsignor wakati wa mauaji yake.

00:37:07.041 --> 00:37:09.166
Na ulikuwa na umiliki wa sanamu ya kichwa cha mbwa mwitu hapo awali

00:37:09.250 --> 00:37:10.666
iliyoambatanishwa na silaha ya mauaji.

00:37:12.500 --> 00:37:14.958
Na wewe ndiye pekee katika kanisa hilo uliyechukia ujasiri wake.

00:37:15.041 --> 00:37:16.875
Mimi… Sichukii ujasiri wowote.

00:37:16.958 --> 00:37:22.166
Lakini haiwezekani kwa mtu yeyote kufanya hivi, kwa hivyo sifanyi hivyo…

00:37:23.750 --> 00:37:26.833
Loo, sijui hii ni nini.

00:37:31.250 --> 00:37:34.250
Sawa. Baba, kwa nini usiende kupumzika?

00:37:34.333 --> 00:37:37.208
Lakini ninapaswa kukuonya kabla ya kuondoka hapa, mji unazungumza.

00:37:37.833 --> 00:37:40.333
Cy Draven aliweka hii kwenye YouTube yake asubuhi ya leo.

00:37:40.416 --> 00:37:42.541
...kuidhuru kanisa hili.

00:37:42.625 --> 00:37:44.750
Nami nitafanya chochote kinachohitajika ili kuiokoa.

00:37:45.291 --> 00:37:49.125
Ili kukukatiza kama saratani.

00:37:50.958 --> 00:37:53.333
Imechapishwa tena.

00:37:54.833 --> 00:37:56.041
Kidogo sana.

00:38:31.208 --> 00:38:35.625
Niliwasha simu yangu kwa dakika mbili, na hilo lilikuwa kosa.

00:38:36.166 --> 00:38:39.666
Mafuriko ya ujumbe kwa kasisi muuaji.

00:38:41.875 --> 00:38:45.541
Lakini sikuwa nafikiria kukamatwa au kuachishwa kazi.

00:38:46.083 --> 00:38:49.916
Nilikuwa nikifikiri Wicks ameshinda.

00:38:51.125 --> 00:38:54.041
Kwa sababu katika sehemu ya roho yangu ambayo haiwezi kumdanganya Kristo,

00:38:54.125 --> 00:38:56.958
au mimi mwenyewe, au wewe…

00:39:00.333 --> 00:39:03.416
...Nilifurahi kwamba mzee alikuwa amekufa.

00:39:11.791 --> 00:39:12.875
Yesu.

00:39:13.708 --> 00:39:16.291
Nisaidie.

00:39:17.333 --> 00:39:19.750
Nionyeshe njia ya kupitia hili, tafadhali.

00:39:24.166 --> 00:39:25.666
Habari?

00:39:29.416 --> 00:39:31.041
Samahani. Um…

00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:33.916
Je, umefungua?

00:39:35.041 --> 00:39:36.125
Daima.

00:39:36.708 --> 00:39:37.916
Uko sawa?

00:39:39.000 --> 00:39:41.500
Ndiyo. Uh-huh. Samahani.

00:39:42.875 --> 00:39:47.791
-Uh, hakuna Misa ya Pasaka. Samahani. -Loo, mimi…

00:39:47.875 --> 00:39:51.541
-Karibu. Karibu. Karibu. -Asante. Asante.

00:39:51.625 --> 00:39:56.041
Sitaki kukuondoa kwenye majukumu yako ya kikuhani sasa, sivyo?

00:39:58.416 --> 00:40:01.166
Naam… Je, hii si kitu?

00:40:01.250 --> 00:40:02.083
Sawa?

00:40:02.166 --> 00:40:06.375
Ni vigumu kuwa hapa ndani na kutohisi uwepo Wake.

00:40:07.000 --> 00:40:08.083
Nani?

00:40:09.041 --> 00:40:12.083
Ee Mungu… Ee. Naam.

00:40:12.166 --> 00:40:13.750
-Ndiyo. -Wewe si Mkatoliki.

00:40:13.833 --> 00:40:16.000
Hapana, sivyo, hapana.

00:40:16.875 --> 00:40:18.291
Mzushi mwenye fahari.

00:40:19.250 --> 00:40:21.458
Ninapiga magoti kwenye madhabahu ya mwenye akili.

00:40:21.541 --> 00:40:24.500
Uh-huh. Hukulelewa katika imani?

00:40:25.250 --> 00:40:27.958
Mama yangu ni… alikuwa, uh,

00:40:28.041 --> 00:40:30.875
mcha Mungu sana, unajua.

00:40:32.583 --> 00:40:34.416
-Je, ulikuwa karibu naye? -Hapana.

00:40:35.250 --> 00:40:39.125
Nilipokuwa mvulana, sisi, um… Lakini ni…

00:40:39.208 --> 00:40:41.208
-Ngumu. Familia. -Ni ngumu.

00:40:41.291 --> 00:40:42.708
Ndiyo. Hiyo ni kweli.

00:40:47.791 --> 00:40:49.500
Haya yote yanakufanya uhisije?

00:40:52.791 --> 00:40:54.625
Inanifanya nihisije?

00:40:59.208 --> 00:41:00.041
Kweli?

00:41:00.125 --> 00:41:01.208
Hakika.

00:41:03.541 --> 00:41:05.375
Naam, usanifu, unaonivutia.

00:41:06.375 --> 00:41:09.583
Ninahisi ukuu,… fumbo,

00:41:09.666 --> 00:41:13.375
athari ya kihisia inayokusudiwa. Ni…

00:41:15.750 --> 00:41:20.958
Na ni kama mtu ameniambia hadithi ambayo siiamini.

00:41:21.833 --> 00:41:25.500
Imejengwa juu ya ahadi tupu ya hadithi ya mtoto

00:41:25.583 --> 00:41:30.250
kujazwa na unyanyasaji, chuki dhidi ya wanawake na chuki dhidi ya mashoga

00:41:30.333 --> 00:41:34.500
na vitendo vyake visivyohesabika vya vurugu na ukatili

00:41:34.583 --> 00:41:36.583
wakati wote, na bado,

00:41:36.666 --> 00:41:39.500
kuficha matendo yake ya aibu.

00:41:39.583 --> 00:41:41.708
Kwa hivyo kama nyumbu mkorofi akipiga teke nyuma,

00:41:41.791 --> 00:41:45.000
Nataka kuitenganisha na kuifungua kiputo chake cha imani cha udanganyifu

00:41:45.083 --> 00:41:50.291
na kufikia ukweli kwamba naweza kumeza bila kusongwa na pumzi.

00:41:57.708 --> 00:42:02.833
Maelezo ya paa ni sawa sana, ingawa. Ni…

00:42:04.500 --> 00:42:07.333
Sikiliza… unataka kunifukuza, endelea moja kwa moja.

00:42:07.416 --> 00:42:08.500
Hapana hapana.

00:42:09.958 --> 00:42:11.625
Unasema kweli, ni vizuri.

00:42:11.708 --> 00:42:15.166
Kusema ukweli kunaweza kuwa jambo la kusumbua.

00:42:15.250 --> 00:42:19.000
Sasa, nadhani huwezi kuwa mwaminifu kila wakati kwa waumini wa kanisa lako.

00:42:19.083 --> 00:42:22.250
Unaweza kuwa mkweli kila wakati kwa kutosema sehemu isiyo ya kweli.

00:42:23.000 --> 00:42:24.875
Ndiyo.

00:42:26.125 --> 00:42:28.125
Uko sahihi. Ni usimulizi wa hadithi.

00:42:29.416 --> 00:42:32.958
Na kanisa hili, ni…si la enzi za kati. Tuko New York.

00:42:33.708 --> 00:42:35.833
Ni karne ya 19 ya Neo-Gothic.

00:42:35.916 --> 00:42:38.458
Inafanana zaidi na Disneyland kuliko Notre-Dame…

00:42:38.541 --> 00:42:40.750
...na ibada na mila

00:42:42.000 --> 00:42:43.625
na mavazi, yote hayo.

00:42:44.458 --> 00:42:45.875
Ni usimulizi wa hadithi.

00:42:47.333 --> 00:42:48.416
Uko sahihi.

00:42:51.291 --> 00:42:52.916
Nadhani swali ni

00:42:54.625 --> 00:42:56.750
Je, hadithi hizi zinatushawishi kuhusu uongo?

00:42:58.625 --> 00:43:02.708
Au zinapatana na kitu kilicho ndani yetu ambacho ni kweli kabisa?

00:43:05.458 --> 00:43:08.125
Kwamba hatuwezi kuelezea kwa njia nyingine yoyote…

00:43:10.416 --> 00:43:11.833
isipokuwa usimulizi wa hadithi.

00:43:15.125 --> 00:43:17.333
Nimeguswa. Padre.

00:43:25.833 --> 00:43:27.250
-Mwanangu. -Samahani.

00:43:28.416 --> 00:43:29.625
Mimi tu…

00:43:30.875 --> 00:43:33.291
Nilihisi kama kuhani tena,

00:43:33.916 --> 00:43:36.041
na sasa nitapoteza hilo na…

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:39.541
na kupoteza kusudi langu na ninaogopa, mimi…

00:43:39.625 --> 00:43:42.125
Sijui nitaishi vipi.

00:43:42.208 --> 00:43:43.291
Blanc!

00:43:44.041 --> 00:43:46.666
Hei! Umempata! Je, yeye…

00:43:55.208 --> 00:43:56.208
Wewe ni nani?

00:43:56.291 --> 00:43:57.916
Labda ningepaswa kuongoza katika hili.

00:43:58.000 --> 00:44:00.083
Jina langu ni Benoit Blanc. Mimi ni mpelelezi.

00:44:00.166 --> 00:44:03.583
Nimevutiwa na mauaji ya Jefferson Wicks.

00:44:04.958 --> 00:44:06.791
Wewe ni mpelelezi, kwa hivyo uko na polisi?

00:44:06.875 --> 00:44:09.083
Hapana, hapana. Ninafanya kazi binafsi.

00:44:09.166 --> 00:44:12.250
Kila mtu anafikiri ni mimi niliyefanya. Sikufanya.

00:44:12.833 --> 00:44:14.875
Lakini moyoni mwangu labda nilifanya hivyo,

00:44:14.958 --> 00:44:17.458
na jinsi ilivyotokea ilikuwa aina fulani ya muujiza.

00:44:17.541 --> 00:44:18.541
Na…

00:44:19.041 --> 00:44:21.541
Sijui. Nimepotea. Sijui.

00:44:22.708 --> 00:44:24.708
Ungeniruhusu nikusaidie?

00:44:27.041 --> 00:44:28.125
Nini?

00:44:28.208 --> 00:44:30.958
Midomo yako imepasuka kwa upungufu wa maji mwilini.

00:44:31.041 --> 00:44:32.458
Hujalala usiku kucha.

00:44:33.041 --> 00:44:34.416
Uliitumia nje ya nyumba,

00:44:34.500 --> 00:44:37.333
kwa hali ya miguu yako ya suruali, magoti yako yakiomba.

00:44:38.083 --> 00:44:41.500
Ninachokiona si mtu mwenye hatia katika mateso,

00:44:42.250 --> 00:44:45.458
lakini mtu asiye na hatia anayeteswa na hatia.

00:44:47.083 --> 00:44:48.291
Acha nikusaidie.

00:44:48.833 --> 00:44:49.708
Vipi?

00:44:49.791 --> 00:44:51.708
Hii ilivaliwa kama muujiza.

00:44:52.208 --> 00:44:55.625
Ni mauaji tu na mimi hutatua mauaji.

00:44:57.500 --> 00:44:59.666
Subiri… Je, ulikuwa

00:45:00.500 --> 00:45:03.666
jambo la Kentucky Derby kuhusu mauaji na jamaa waliyemkamata

00:45:03.750 --> 00:45:05.250
-na kamera ya kumalizia picha? -Ndiyo.

00:45:05.333 --> 00:45:06.416
Kwa hivyo wewe ni…

00:45:07.250 --> 00:45:08.458
Ulikuwa kwenye The View.

00:45:08.541 --> 00:45:10.166
-Ndiyo. -Unafanya nini hapa?

00:45:10.250 --> 00:45:14.000
Nahitaji kuja haraka ili niweze kuhudhuria hafla za ibada ya Ijumaa Kuu.

00:45:14.083 --> 00:45:17.041
na mambo yanayoendelea hapa katika Our Lady of Perpetual Fortiness.

00:45:17.708 --> 00:45:20.583
Geraldine ameniruhusu kwa neema kuingia.

00:45:20.666 --> 00:45:24.750
Kama unaweza kupumzika na kunisindikiza katika uchunguzi wangu,

00:45:25.375 --> 00:45:28.541
tazama mwili, fuatilia silaha ya mauaji, chunguza eneo la uhalifu,

00:45:28.625 --> 00:45:32.125
Uko katika nafasi ya kipekee ya kunisaidia.

00:45:33.791 --> 00:45:35.000
Mwili?

00:45:40.916 --> 00:45:43.625
Ndiyo, nimebadilisha mawazo yangu. Sidhani kama ninapaswa kuwa hapa.

00:45:44.708 --> 00:45:47.333
Blanc, ninaamini mchakato wako, lakini nakubaliana naye.

00:45:47.416 --> 00:45:51.500
Hapana, hapana, hapana. Nataka upate picha wazi ya kliniki ya kile kilichotokea hapa.

00:45:51.583 --> 00:45:55.666
Kumwona Wicks jinsi alivyo, maiti. Chombo kitupu tu.

00:45:55.750 --> 00:45:59.208
Sio mnyama wa kizushi akilini mwako, bali ni nyama na damu tu.

00:45:59.291 --> 00:46:01.708
Tunaweza kuchanganua amekufa kutokana na jeraha la kisu.

00:46:01.791 --> 00:46:04.541
Tu… nyama na damu.

00:46:05.208 --> 00:46:06.500
Nyama na damu, ndio.

00:46:06.583 --> 00:46:09.250
Ndiyo, hiyo ndiyo tabia yetu ya kutetemeka.

00:46:09.833 --> 00:46:12.041
-Ndiyo. Angalia hilo. -Tafadhali acha kufanya hivyo.

00:46:13.125 --> 00:46:15.791
-Tammy. Ungependa kugeuza nyama? -Mm.

00:46:15.875 --> 00:46:17.416
-Mpe keki. Ndiyo. -Mm-hmm.

00:46:21.958 --> 00:46:23.583
Moja, mbili, tatu.

00:46:29.500 --> 00:46:32.625
-Hei! Hei. -Hapana, hapana, hapana. Mimi si wa hapa.

00:46:32.708 --> 00:46:35.083
Siwezi kuwa hapa ndani, sijui kwa nini ulinileta.

00:46:35.166 --> 00:46:36.208
-Siwezi-- -Hei!

00:46:37.416 --> 00:46:38.833
Ukitaka msamaha,

00:46:38.916 --> 00:46:42.375
Unataka kuwa kuhani tena, basi unahitaji kupitia hili pamoja nami.

00:46:42.458 --> 00:46:46.125
Muuaji halisi yuko nje. Lazima tumtafute, tumpigie misumari, mimi…

00:46:46.208 --> 00:46:47.041
Samahani.

00:46:47.125 --> 00:46:50.041
Namaanisha, mkamate na upate maisha yako tena.

00:46:50.125 --> 00:46:51.333
Baba.

00:46:52.083 --> 00:46:54.416
Nahitaji kujua unaelewa hali hiyo.

00:46:54.500 --> 00:46:57.833
Sisi sote si marafiki wanaozunguka-zunguka wakijaribu kutatua kesi.

00:46:57.916 --> 00:46:59.541
Bado wewe ni mtuhumiwa.

00:46:59.625 --> 00:47:03.708
Jambo kuu ni kwamba, huhitaji kuwa hapa bila wakili, unaelewa hilo?

00:47:05.583 --> 00:47:08.333
Sikufanya hivi.

00:47:09.583 --> 00:47:11.250
Kama naweza kusaidia kujua ni nani aliyefanya hivyo,

00:47:11.916 --> 00:47:14.458
kisha mimi huingia, ndio, tufanye hivyo, ndio.

00:47:14.541 --> 00:47:15.750
Sawa.

00:47:16.625 --> 00:47:17.833
Mwili.

00:47:17.916 --> 00:47:19.500
Ifuatayo ni silaha ya mauaji.

00:47:19.583 --> 00:47:20.666
Kisha eneo la uhalifu.

00:47:21.958 --> 00:47:23.375
Shikamana nami.

00:47:30.125 --> 00:47:32.750
Nitakuambia kitu, simpendi hata shetani.

00:47:32.833 --> 00:47:36.916
Unajua, Il Diavolo, inasikika ya kifahari, Kiitaliano, hiyo ni sawa, unajua,

00:47:37.000 --> 00:47:39.125
kisha mke wangu, ananunua ishara ya shetani,

00:47:39.208 --> 00:47:41.125
