00:47:44.875 --> 00:47:48.500
Na kisha, unajua, uh, shetani, shetani, shetani, kishindo, sijui.

00:47:48.583 --> 00:47:50.958
-Lakini hiyo… Lakini hiyo ndiyo yote, sivyo? -Ndiyo.

00:47:51.041 --> 00:47:52.166
Loo, ndio.

00:47:52.250 --> 00:47:55.125
Lakini, uh…

00:47:55.208 --> 00:47:58.708
Lakini unajua, haikuwa nyekundu ingawa, sasa ni nyekundu, ni rangi.

00:47:58.791 --> 00:48:01.166
-Ndiyo, ndiyo, imepakwa rangi mpya. -Natumai. Hmm.

00:48:01.750 --> 00:48:05.375
Waliijaza aina fulani ya plasta na wakachomeka blade kwa njia hiyo.

00:48:05.458 --> 00:48:07.833
Nitafanya chochote kinachohitajika ili kuiokoa.

00:48:07.916 --> 00:48:11.125
Ili kukukatiza kama saratani.

00:48:11.208 --> 00:48:14.458
Hujambo, hujambo. Njoo, ixnay. Hilo si jambo zuri. Njoo.

00:48:14.541 --> 00:48:16.833
Jambo la kichwa cha shetani chekundu, hilo liliishia wapi?

00:48:16.916 --> 00:48:21.500
Kanisani, niliitupa kanisani na ikavunja dirisha, sijui ni kwa nini.

00:48:23.083 --> 00:48:25.291
Na kisha baada ya Misa ya Krismasi Jumatatu,

00:48:25.375 --> 00:48:27.708
Martha alisema alipata dirisha dogo lililovunjika.

00:48:27.791 --> 00:48:28.791
Watoto.

00:48:28.875 --> 00:48:30.291
Lakini hakuna kingine.

00:48:30.375 --> 00:48:33.166
Najua tatizo ni nini, silichanganyi

00:48:34.541 --> 00:48:36.750
Ninachojaribu kusema ni kwamba

00:48:36.833 --> 00:48:39.250
Kwa nini shetani awe na muziki mzuri wote?

00:48:39.916 --> 00:48:42.333
Ninajisikia vizuri kila siku

00:48:44.166 --> 00:48:47.583
Kwa sababu Yesu ndiye mwamba Na aliondoa huzuni zangu

00:48:48.666 --> 00:48:49.958
Unaona hilo?

00:48:50.041 --> 00:48:52.708
Wanasema nikate nywele zangu Wananifanya niwe mwendawazimu…

00:48:53.583 --> 00:48:54.500
Hmm.

00:48:56.083 --> 00:48:56.958
Ndiyo.

00:48:58.625 --> 00:48:59.708
Ndiyo.

00:49:03.375 --> 00:49:05.375
Loo. Hiyo ni, uh…

00:49:07.708 --> 00:49:08.916
Dkt. Nat.

00:49:10.291 --> 00:49:11.500
Loo, f…

00:49:13.791 --> 00:49:15.875
Habari.

00:49:17.791 --> 00:49:19.208
Kula chakula cha mchana tu.

00:49:25.750 --> 00:49:29.375
Nat, mimi… naweza kuja baadaye ikiwa… ikiwa unataka kuzungumza.

00:49:29.458 --> 00:49:31.583
Sidhani… Ndiyo, mimi… Ndiyo.

00:49:31.666 --> 00:49:33.583
Sidhani kama ningependelea hivyo.

00:49:33.666 --> 00:49:35.083
Ningependelea isiwe hivyo.

00:49:35.833 --> 00:49:39.083
Ah, hiyo hapo. Hivi ndivyo ulivyotumia. Huh?

00:49:39.625 --> 00:49:41.791
-Njoo, Nat. -"Mkate kama saratani."

00:49:41.875 --> 00:49:43.666
Wewe mwana wa mbwa mwitu.

00:49:43.750 --> 00:49:45.375
-Unamwambia, Nat. -Ndiyo.

00:49:46.583 --> 00:49:49.708
Mwana wa mbwa mwitu! Kasisi muuaji!

00:50:22.166 --> 00:50:23.083
Kwanza kabisa,

00:50:23.166 --> 00:50:26.125
Ninadaiwa na Detective Elliott kikapu cha matunda kwa kunipa namba yako.

00:50:26.208 --> 00:50:28.041
Ninafurahi tu kuwa mhudumu.

00:50:28.125 --> 00:50:29.958
Geraldine, ulikuwa na mtazamo wa mbele

00:50:30.041 --> 00:50:32.625
kuona kwamba hii inazidi kazi ya kawaida ya polisi,

00:50:32.708 --> 00:50:36.958
Hili ni jambo ambalo hata mimi sijapata.

00:50:37.041 --> 00:50:41.125
Mfano wa kitabu cha kiada wa uhalifu usiowezekana kabisa.

00:50:41.958 --> 00:50:43.583
Mambo ya hadithi za upelelezi.

00:50:43.666 --> 00:50:47.000
Hili halipaswi kuwepo katika ulimwengu wetu halisi.

00:50:48.041 --> 00:50:49.458
Na bado iko hapa.

00:50:50.000 --> 00:50:51.416
Utukufu mtakatifu.

00:50:52.500 --> 00:50:53.750
Ninapenda shauku.

00:50:53.833 --> 00:50:56.333
Nahitaji tu kujisikia na uhakika unajua kesi hii inaweza kutatuliwa.

00:50:56.416 --> 00:50:58.708
Sina uwezo wa kutosuluhisha uhalifu.

00:50:59.458 --> 00:51:01.083
Wakati huo wa mlinzi

00:51:01.958 --> 00:51:05.375
ninapopanda jukwaani na kufungua mtandao wa mpinzani wangu…

00:51:07.125 --> 00:51:08.416
Loo, utaona. Ni furaha!

00:51:09.000 --> 00:51:11.166
-Sawa, tunafikaje huko? -Chanzo,

00:51:12.000 --> 00:51:14.583
John Dickson Carr's The Hollow Man.

00:51:15.375 --> 00:51:17.625
Riwaya ya upelelezi ya Enzi ya Dhahabu

00:51:17.708 --> 00:51:19.833
na utangulizi halisi juu ya fumbo la mlango uliofungwa,

00:51:19.916 --> 00:51:21.208
uhalifu usiowezekana.

00:51:22.958 --> 00:51:24.041
Simama.

00:51:32.375 --> 00:51:35.875
Baba Jud, tena, akipata riziki yako.

00:51:37.541 --> 00:51:40.166
Mwili wa Nani? Mauaji katika Chumba cha Kuhifadhia Maiti cha Mtaa.

00:51:40.250 --> 00:51:42.666
Roger Ackroyd. Mauaji katika Vicarage.

00:51:42.750 --> 00:51:47.958
Mungu wangu, huu ni mtaala wa jinsi ya kufanya uhalifu huu.

00:51:48.458 --> 00:51:50.375
Na kundi lote liko katika kundi hili?

00:51:54.000 --> 00:51:55.625
Nani alichagua vitabu hivi?

00:51:56.291 --> 00:51:57.125
Oprah.

00:51:58.333 --> 00:51:59.333
Oprah.

00:51:59.833 --> 00:52:01.916
Martha anachora orodha ya mada kutoka kwenye tovuti ya Oprah.

00:52:02.000 --> 00:52:03.833
Naam, hii inathibitisha nadharia yangu.

00:52:04.416 --> 00:52:06.333
Muuaji hakika aliiga

00:52:06.416 --> 00:52:09.166
mbinu za kitamaduni za hadithi ya fumbo iliyofungwa.

00:52:09.708 --> 00:52:11.916
Ambayo hurahisisha mambo.

00:52:12.000 --> 00:52:13.208
Muda wa klabu ya vitabu.

00:52:13.750 --> 00:52:15.166
Njooni, watoto.

00:52:21.833 --> 00:52:24.166
Katika The Hollow Man, mpelelezi Gideon Fell

00:52:24.250 --> 00:52:29.166
inatoa muhtasari wa njia zote zinazowezekana za mauaji ya mlango uliofungwa.

00:52:29.250 --> 00:52:31.375
Kwa hivyo tuwapange kwenye mstari na kuwaangusha chini.

00:52:31.458 --> 00:52:33.583
Uwezekano namba moja,

00:52:33.666 --> 00:52:37.083
Wicks alichomwa kisu

00:52:37.708 --> 00:52:40.041
kabla ya kuingia kabatini.

00:52:40.625 --> 00:52:44.041
Baba Jud, je, ungechukua nafasi yako hapo ulipo?

00:52:47.208 --> 00:52:49.333
Wicks anakamilisha mahubiri yake.

00:52:51.083 --> 00:52:52.750
Kifaa chochote nyuma yake

00:52:52.833 --> 00:52:57.833
mwenye uwezo wa kusukuma kisu kizito kisicho na usawa mgongoni mwake…

00:53:00.791 --> 00:53:04.875
ingekuwa imefichwa kutoka kwa kamera na mashahidi waliokuwa ndani ya meli,

00:53:05.500 --> 00:53:09.000
lakini bila shaka ingeshuhudiwa na Padre Jud.

00:53:10.625 --> 00:53:13.666
Hapana, sikuona roboti ya kupiga visu nyuma yake.

00:53:13.750 --> 00:53:16.291
Hapana. Uwezekano wa kwanza, umekwama.

00:53:16.375 --> 00:53:18.208
Uwezekano wa pili…

00:53:20.083 --> 00:53:21.500
Aliuawa

00:53:22.000 --> 00:53:23.833
akiwa ndani ya kabati

00:53:23.916 --> 00:53:27.541
na mtu au kitu ambacho kilikuwa

00:53:28.291 --> 00:53:30.125
nje ya kabati.

00:53:30.833 --> 00:53:34.416
Kama, kitu kilipiga kisu kwenye kabati kutoka hapa nje?

00:53:34.500 --> 00:53:35.916
Hapana, hiyo ni upuuzi.

00:53:36.000 --> 00:53:38.000
Karanga na haiwezekani kwa pande kadhaa.

00:53:38.083 --> 00:53:41.083
Uwezekano wa pili, umekwama. Maendeleo!

00:53:41.166 --> 00:53:43.250
Kuna uwezekano gani zaidi?

00:53:43.333 --> 00:53:45.333
Sio nyingi. Tatu…

00:53:46.166 --> 00:53:49.041
Aliuawa akiwa ndani ya kabati

00:53:49.125 --> 00:53:51.750
kwa kifaa ambacho pia kilikuwa

00:53:53.041 --> 00:53:54.541
ndani ya kabati.

00:53:54.625 --> 00:53:56.833
Kwa hivyo kitu kiliwekwa mapema na,

00:53:56.916 --> 00:53:58.541
nini, kinachosababishwa na kidhibiti cha mbali?

00:53:58.625 --> 00:54:00.625
Naam, kuta hizi ni nene,

00:54:00.708 --> 00:54:04.125
lakini ishara kali sana ya RF inaweza kupenya ndani yao.

00:54:04.875 --> 00:54:07.083
Kwa hivyo mtu angejificha wapi…

00:54:07.625 --> 00:54:12.041
...kifaa cha kusukuma kisu kinachodhibitiwa kwa mbali kinachofanya kazi kikamilifu

00:54:12.583 --> 00:54:14.333
katika sanduku tupu, mm?

00:54:15.125 --> 00:54:16.875
Wicks alianguka tumboni mwake.

00:54:16.958 --> 00:54:19.666
Nakumbuka ule mlio mkali.

00:54:21.583 --> 00:54:24.083
Na uso wake ulikuwa ukielekea mlangoni,

00:54:24.166 --> 00:54:26.125
kwa hivyo alikuwa amesimama nyuma akiangalia nje,

00:54:27.166 --> 00:54:30.583
kwa hivyo kisu lazima kingepitia ukuta wa nyuma.

00:54:31.083 --> 00:54:33.500
Kishindo cha Clangy. Nzuri sana.

00:54:34.041 --> 00:54:35.250
Hata hivyo,

00:54:36.250 --> 00:54:38.125
Mwamba wa Gibraltar.

00:54:38.958 --> 00:54:40.041
Vipi kuhusu…

00:54:40.541 --> 00:54:43.125
Vipi kuhusu ukuta bandia ulioondolewa baadaye?

00:54:43.208 --> 00:54:45.166
Nenda mjini, Baba Brown.

00:54:45.250 --> 00:54:46.708
Nini? Hapana, hapana.

00:54:46.791 --> 00:54:48.875
Wavulana wangu wangegundua ukuta bandia.

00:54:52.750 --> 00:54:56.583
Ndiyo. Na kuiondoa baadaye isingekuwa kazi ndogo.

00:54:58.416 --> 00:55:01.166
Hakuna kitu kingine kilichopatikana kwenye sakafu ya nafasi hii, sivyo?

00:55:01.833 --> 00:55:04.458
Hapana. Hapana, uzi mwekundu tu.

00:55:06.500 --> 00:55:07.916
Subiri, nini?…

00:55:08.000 --> 00:55:09.708
Uzi mwekundu?

00:55:11.666 --> 00:55:15.291
Nyuzi mbili nene nyekundu zenye urefu wa inchi tatu, zilipatikana hapo

00:55:15.375 --> 00:55:17.375
karibu na mwili karibu na nyonga.

00:55:19.333 --> 00:55:20.916
Kwa hivyo, uwezekano wa nne ni nini?

00:55:26.125 --> 00:55:27.208
Martha?

00:55:28.166 --> 00:55:30.375
-Watupe nje. -Martha?

00:55:30.458 --> 00:55:31.750
Watupe nje!

00:55:31.833 --> 00:55:35.083
Kutembea mahali hapa patakatifu

00:55:35.166 --> 00:55:38.500
kama eneo la uhalifu. Kama baadhi

00:55:38.583 --> 00:55:42.208
Onyesho la polisi wa kipuuzi likizungumzia roboti!

00:55:42.791 --> 00:55:46.291
Sio sawa, Baba, si sawa, si sawa!

00:55:48.916 --> 00:55:51.541
Martha, unapaswa kwenda nyumbani, pumzika kidogo.

00:55:52.083 --> 00:55:53.208
Je, ninaweza kukufanyia chochote?

00:55:54.041 --> 00:55:55.083
Ondoka.

00:55:55.791 --> 00:55:57.625
Hakuna anayekutaka hapa tena.

00:55:58.125 --> 00:56:03.000
Umemchukia Monsignor siku zote na huna chochote ila dharau kwetu.

00:56:03.083 --> 00:56:05.500
-Hiyo si kweli. -Mauaji moyoni mwako...

00:56:05.583 --> 00:56:07.208
-Hapana. -…damu mikononi mwako

00:56:07.291 --> 00:56:09.291
kama vile kahaba kahaba.

00:56:09.375 --> 00:56:12.583
Dhambi yako ya asili imechafua mahali hapa.

00:56:13.333 --> 00:56:15.083
Kuhani wa uongo!

00:56:17.958 --> 00:56:19.541
Samahani.

00:56:20.375 --> 00:56:22.541
Lakini, ndio, kama kutafuta ukweli na mpelelezi huyo

00:56:22.625 --> 00:56:24.791
ananiweka dhidi yako na kundi hili basi na iwe hivyo.

00:56:27.583 --> 00:56:28.666
Samahani.

00:56:39.541 --> 00:56:41.291
Naweza kutumia begi lako?

00:56:42.791 --> 00:56:44.416
Hakika. Endelea.

00:56:47.958 --> 00:56:49.375
Uko sawa?

00:56:50.000 --> 00:56:53.375
Ukungu ulikuwa unafunguka. Hili lilikuwa fumbo ambalo lingeweza kutatuliwa.

00:56:53.458 --> 00:56:56.083
Mwili, silaha, eneo la uhalifu, bunduki za roboti,

00:56:56.166 --> 00:56:59.208
na pembe za mtazamo na kuta za mawe na vidhibiti vya mbali.

00:57:01.666 --> 00:57:02.958
Na vidhibiti vya mbali.

00:57:03.041 --> 00:57:06.500
Lakini ni siku mpya... Watoto wa Kike...

00:57:06.583 --> 00:57:09.333
Nani angekuwa shujaa katika mchezo huo...

