Kufunga cheo, kumtia aibu

01:10:39.708 --> 01:10:42.125
na kutufundisha sote kumwaibisha.

01:10:44.000 --> 01:10:45.416
Msichana huyo maskini.

01:10:51.791 --> 01:10:56.625
Jana, nilipigiwa simu na mfanyakazi mwenzangu wa sheria za familia huko Brooklyn.

01:10:57.375 --> 01:11:00.583
Alitaka kuangalia tena maelezo ya mawasiliano

01:11:00.666 --> 01:11:04.375
kwa Monsignor Jefferson Wicks, mteja wangu,

01:11:04.458 --> 01:11:08.541
kwa sababu mteja wangu alikuwa amewasilisha AOP kwake.

01:11:09.500 --> 01:11:10.708
Huko Brooklyn.

01:11:11.458 --> 01:11:13.666
Kwa hivyo nisingejua.

01:11:14.708 --> 01:11:16.250
AOP ni nini?

01:11:19.625 --> 01:11:22.041
"Utambuzi wa uzazi"?

01:11:25.375 --> 01:11:28.166
"Uthibitisho kwamba mimi, Jefferson Wicks,

01:11:28.250 --> 01:11:31.625
Mimi ni baba mzazi wa Cyrus Draven."

01:11:36.666 --> 01:11:39.083
Hakuna aibu kwako.

01:11:40.125 --> 01:11:42.041
Sawa?

01:11:42.125 --> 01:11:43.666
Mama alikuwa nani?

01:11:45.208 --> 01:11:46.833
Je, ina maana hata kidogo?

01:11:47.458 --> 01:11:53.291
Hapana. Hapana! Hapana, alirudi na kumwacha mtoto huyu maskini mapajani mwako.

01:11:53.916 --> 01:11:56.250
Na kisha akaenda na kuishi maisha marefu.

01:11:56.333 --> 01:11:59.833
Na baba yangu mwaminifu alinisaidia.

01:11:59.916 --> 01:12:04.250
Kwa mara nyingine tena, klabu ya wavulana ilifungamana na hapo ndipo nilipo, mjinga mdogo mwaminifu.

01:12:04.333 --> 01:12:05.541
Imenaswa.

01:12:05.625 --> 01:12:10.875
Nami nilitii na kumheshimu na kumlea mwanao

01:12:10.958 --> 01:12:14.041
huku ukiwa umekaa kwenye mimbari yako, bila haya.

01:12:14.125 --> 01:12:17.916
Wewe… mwana wa mnafiki!

01:12:23.000 --> 01:12:24.083
Nini?

01:12:24.708 --> 01:12:25.708
Ulijua?

01:12:25.791 --> 01:12:27.791
Sio hadi Vera aliponiambia asubuhi ya leo.

01:12:28.458 --> 01:12:29.375
Ndiyo.

01:12:30.291 --> 01:12:31.916
Cy ni mwanangu.

01:12:34.625 --> 01:12:36.458
Kutoka kwa mwanamke mzembe asiye na umuhimu

01:12:36.541 --> 01:12:39.333
ambaye nilimjua kwa usiku mmoja na sijamuona kwa miaka 30.

01:12:39.416 --> 01:12:42.416
Mimi na baba yake Vera tuliweka siri hii. Lakini sivyo tena.

01:12:42.958 --> 01:12:44.625
Yeye ndiye mrithi wangu.

01:12:46.041 --> 01:12:47.125
Mwanangu.

01:12:49.625 --> 01:12:51.750
Sasa dunia itajua hilo.

01:12:53.208 --> 01:12:55.416
Kwa hivyo, panya,

01:12:56.500 --> 01:12:57.791
kukimbia meli inayozama.

01:13:01.166 --> 01:13:02.625
Loo, kata uchafu.

01:13:02.708 --> 01:13:04.500
Nyote mmesimama kando ya mtu wenu.

01:13:04.583 --> 01:13:07.875
Nilitaka tu kuiona. Nilitaka kujionea mwenyewe.

01:13:07.958 --> 01:13:10.875
Unakula uchafu wake kwa kijiko na unarudi kwa sekunde chache.

01:13:10.958 --> 01:13:12.750
Hiyo ni aina ya dharau, Vera.

01:13:12.833 --> 01:13:14.791
-Hujui tunachohisi. -Loo.

01:13:14.875 --> 01:13:18.916
Nadhani sote, kama Wakristo, tumeshtushwa sana na ulichosema.

01:13:20.916 --> 01:13:23.625
Lakini tunapigana vita vya kuwepo hapa

01:13:23.708 --> 01:13:25.750
ambapo mwisho huhalalisha njia.

01:13:25.833 --> 01:13:27.666
Kanisa halihitaji mchumba ambaye atafanya hivyo

01:13:27.750 --> 01:13:29.791
Lala chini na uichukue, tunahitaji shujaa.

01:13:29.875 --> 01:13:31.500
Tunahitaji shujaa

01:13:31.583 --> 01:13:35.666
na naamini kwamba Mungu alimchagua Monsignor Wicks kuwa shujaa wake.

01:13:36.416 --> 01:13:39.250
Kwa hivyo, wewe na mwanao mna upanga wangu.

01:13:39.958 --> 01:13:41.000
Na…

01:13:42.083 --> 01:13:43.708
Hatumjui mwanamke huyu.

01:13:44.708 --> 01:13:46.333
Hatumjui.

01:13:46.916 --> 01:13:49.541
Hatujui, sawa, jinsi alivyo…

01:13:51.541 --> 01:13:54.166
Ukweli ni nini? Sivyo? Kwa vyanzo mbalimbali.

01:13:54.250 --> 01:13:56.708
Hatujui hilo… Hatujui… Ni nini kilichopo?

01:13:56.791 --> 01:13:58.416
Je, kuna yoyote kati ya haya?

01:13:58.500 --> 01:14:01.125
Kwa hivyo…

01:14:01.208 --> 01:14:02.500
Umesema vyema, Daktari.

01:14:02.583 --> 01:14:03.750
Asante.

01:14:04.458 --> 01:14:07.083
Uliahidi kwamba kama ningebaki nawe, ungeweza kuniponya.

01:14:08.291 --> 01:14:09.500
Kama hiyo ni kweli,

01:14:10.041 --> 01:14:11.666
Sihitaji wewe kuwa mtakatifu.

01:14:12.166 --> 01:14:13.708
Tuko pamoja nawe, Monsignor Wicks.

01:14:14.375 --> 01:14:18.833
Na kwa kweli hakuna chochote unachosema au kufanya kitakachobadilisha hilo.

01:14:25.916 --> 01:14:28.666
Nitatoa huduma yangu ya mwisho

01:14:30.083 --> 01:14:32.500
wiki moja kuanzia leo Jumapili ya Pasaka.

01:14:33.791 --> 01:14:35.208
Na kisha

01:14:35.958 --> 01:14:39.875
Nitafunga milango ya kanisa hili dogo la huzuni milele.

01:14:43.250 --> 01:14:47.500
Lakini si kabla sijawaangamiza kila mmoja wenu.

01:14:50.750 --> 01:14:51.958
Samahani. Subiri, nini?

01:14:52.041 --> 01:14:53.458
Unakunywa pombe, Nat?

01:14:53.541 --> 01:14:54.750
Ndiyo. Nini?

01:14:54.833 --> 01:14:56.583
Loo, wewe ni mtu hatari.

01:14:57.333 --> 01:14:58.750
Kwenda kazini nimelewa.

01:14:58.833 --> 01:15:01.916
Kuwatibu wagonjwa, watoto, wakiwa wamelewa.

01:15:02.708 --> 01:15:04.541
Jumuiya hii inapaswa kujua.

01:15:04.625 --> 01:15:06.708
Bodi ya matibabu inapaswa kujua.

01:15:06.791 --> 01:15:11.166
Hakuna mtu anayepaswa kukuamini au kukuajiri tena.

01:15:11.791 --> 01:15:12.875
Na, Lee.

01:15:13.500 --> 01:15:16.500
Kitabu hiki cha Troubadour ambacho umekuwa ukikiandika.

01:15:16.583 --> 01:15:21.291
Ujinga wake wa kupindukia ni aibu kwa huduma yangu.

01:15:21.375 --> 01:15:25.208
Ni… Ni wajibu wangu kuwaonya si umma tu bali…

01:15:25.291 --> 01:15:27.291
...marafiki zangu katika ulimwengu wa uchapishaji.

01:15:27.375 --> 01:15:30.250
Lazima izikwe. Lazima uzikwe.

01:15:30.833 --> 01:15:34.458
Umefichuliwa kama mcheshi asiye na maana kama ulivyo.

01:15:34.541 --> 01:15:36.958
Nini hasa? Ni nini kinachoendelea sasa hivi?

01:15:37.041 --> 01:15:38.125
Na, Vera.

01:15:38.666 --> 01:15:41.000
Wewe ni ndoto mbaya ya baba yako.

01:15:41.791 --> 01:15:43.416
Angeona aibu sana.

01:15:45.333 --> 01:15:48.416
Simone. Siwezi kumponya mwanamke asiye na imani.

01:15:49.125 --> 01:15:50.541
Siwezi kukusaidia.

01:15:50.625 --> 01:15:53.125
Ulisema unaweza kunifukuza.

01:15:53.208 --> 01:15:55.000
Mm, sikukuahidi chochote.

01:15:56.166 --> 01:15:58.791
Nimekupa akiba yangu yote.

01:15:58.875 --> 01:16:00.958
Huwezi kununua uponyaji wa Mungu.

01:16:01.750 --> 01:16:03.583
Hutaponywa kamwe.

01:16:03.666 --> 01:16:06.500
Utakufa kwa maumivu katika gereza la kiti hicho.

01:16:07.125 --> 01:16:10.166
Kwa nini unafanya hivi? Sielewi.

01:16:10.250 --> 01:16:13.416
-Huu ni utani. Sivyo? Utani. -Nimechanganyikiwa sana.

01:16:13.500 --> 01:16:16.750
Je, hii ni malipo kwa mkutano wa maombi wa Baba Jud kwa sababu alituvizia?

01:16:16.833 --> 01:16:18.416
Mkutano wa maombi wa Baba Jud?

01:16:19.875 --> 01:16:21.791
Nimehifadhi kanisa hili.

01:16:21.875 --> 01:16:24.000
Nimeiimarisha kwa ukweli wa Mungu.

01:16:24.083 --> 01:16:27.916
Na sasa usaliti wa kupata mamlaka yangu

01:16:28.000 --> 01:16:31.291
na imani na maisha yenyewe yalipingwa…

01:16:31.375 --> 01:16:33.791
...na kutoka ndani ya patakatifu pangu!

01:16:36.333 --> 01:16:37.541
Toka nje!

01:16:39.500 --> 01:16:41.750
Dhaifu.

01:16:42.583 --> 01:16:44.000
Ninyi nyote.

01:16:44.083 --> 01:16:46.291
Huwezi kufuata njia yangu.

01:16:46.375 --> 01:16:48.583
Ndiyo, tuko vitani

01:16:48.666 --> 01:16:51.125
nami nitawatupa nje ya ngome yangu.

01:16:51.708 --> 01:16:52.916
Wewe mwana wa mbwa mwitu.

01:16:53.000 --> 01:16:55.875
Siku ya Jumapili ya Pasaka, wakati viti vya kuketi vitakapojaa watu wa mjini,

01:16:55.958 --> 01:16:58.375
Nitafunua dhambi za kundi hili.

01:16:58.458 --> 01:17:02.875
Kata wewe na ukung'ute vumbi la mahali hapa kutoka kwenye viatu vyangu.

01:17:04.083 --> 01:17:05.291
Na kuzimu

01:17:06.625 --> 01:17:07.708
pamoja nanyi nyote.

01:17:21.416 --> 01:17:25.583
Naam, utukufu uwe. Hilo lilisafisha chumba.

01:17:25.666 --> 01:17:26.750
Cy.

01:17:28.041 --> 01:17:30.125
Kwa nini alifanya hivyo?

01:17:30.208 --> 01:17:32.458
Cy. Niambie. Nini kilikuwa kikiendelea?

01:17:32.541 --> 01:17:34.916
Kwa nini aliwachoma wote? Kwa nini angefanya hivyo?

01:17:35.000 --> 01:17:36.333
Kwa sababu nilimwambia afanye hivyo.

01:17:37.291 --> 01:17:39.916
Vera aliponiambia ukweli, nilienda na kumpata.

01:17:40.791 --> 01:17:44.000
Na alinikumbatia kama mwana kwa mara ya kwanza maishani mwangu.

01:17:44.750 --> 01:17:46.666
Alijifungua mzigo.

01:17:47.375 --> 01:17:49.375
Nachukia mahali hapa.

01:17:50.541 --> 01:17:52.958
Nachukia kundi hili la walioshindwa kwa huzuni.

01:17:53.791 --> 01:17:55.416
Nataka kutoka nje.

01:17:56.208 --> 01:17:57.833
Na sasa, hatimaye…

01:17:58.958 --> 01:18:00.166
Naweza.

01:18:01.958 --> 01:18:03.166
Aliniambia,

01:18:03.958 --> 01:18:06.791
utajiri wa familia ya babu yake, uliopotea miaka hii yote,

01:18:06.875 --> 01:18:09.083
Aliniambia ameipata. Wiki hii tu.

01:18:09.166 --> 01:18:11.000
Hapana. Hapana, pesa hizo zimepotea.

01:18:11.083 --> 01:18:14.791
Hakuna anayejua Prentice aliiweka wapi, lakini imetoweka bila dalili yoyote.

01:18:14.875 --> 01:18:17.500
Aliniambia ameipata.

01:18:17.583 --> 01:18:20.625
Angefunga jalala hili na kustaafu katika utajiri mchafu.

01:18:21.291 --> 01:18:24.416
Nami nikamwambia, "Umechanganyikiwa?"

01:18:24.500 --> 01:18:27.291
Kustaafu? Je, unajua nguvu ya kile unachofanya kwenye jukwaa hilo?

01:18:27.375 --> 01:18:28.625
Nimepunguza kundi.

01:18:28.708 --> 01:18:30.375
Hapana. Umewafanya kuwa na msimamo mkali.

01:18:31.041 --> 01:18:32.083
Hiyo ndiyo nguvu.

01:18:32.875 --> 01:18:36.875
Katika mji mdogo, kuna wachawi wachache tu wa kuwachoma na wakereketwa wa kuwaamsha.

01:18:36.958 --> 01:18:39.375
Mwali wako hauna mafuta.

01:18:39.458 --> 01:18:40.875
Lakini kwenye mtandao,

01:18:41.375 --> 01:18:42.583
moto wa porini.

01:18:43.875 --> 01:18:45.083
Pesa hii.

01:18:45.875 --> 01:18:48.708
Utu wako wa ibada. Unanitania?

01:18:48.791 --> 01:18:50.333
Nipe miaka minne.

01:18:50.416 --> 01:18:51.833
Unaweza kuwa rais.

01:18:52.916 --> 01:18:55.041
Pamoja tunaweza kujenga himaya halisi.

01:18:56.250 --> 01:18:59.250
Kama baba na mwana.

01:19:01.666 --> 01:19:03.083
Kama ilivyo katika Star Wars?

01:19:03.166 --> 01:19:05.958
-Ndiyo. Hasa, kama Waasi. -Oh.

01:19:06.041 --> 01:19:09.458
Huduma yake na hisia zangu za kisiasa zilichochewa na pesa za kutosha.

01:19:09.541 --> 01:19:11.833
Je, unaweza kufikiria kile tunachoweza kufanya katika jina la Kristo?

01:19:12.500 --> 01:19:14.125
Ndiyo. Ndiyo, nadhani naweza.

01:19:14.208 --> 01:19:17.541
Kwanza, nilimwambia, na nitakubali hili ni jambo la kibinafsi kidogo,

01:19:17.625 --> 01:19:20.375
Kwanza nilimwambia tunahitaji kuchoma kundi hili.

01:19:20.458 --> 01:19:21.833
Wao ni dhima.

01:19:21.916 --> 01:19:24.041
Kama wakijihusisha nasi,

01:19:24.125 --> 01:19:27.000
kujitokeza kwenye habari za cable, hata unataka nafasi katika jambo hili...

01:19:27.083 --> 01:19:29.333
Tunahitaji kuwachoma kama ruba.

01:19:30.250 --> 01:19:31.875
Ndiyo maana aliwachoma wote.

01:19:32.541 --> 01:19:34.375
Kwa sababu ya kisasi chako kidogo.

01:19:34.958 --> 01:19:37.500
Huenda mmoja wao alimwua kwa ajili yake. Unajua hilo, sivyo?

01:19:38.083 --> 01:19:40.916
Kurudi kwenye bahati hii kubwa.

01:19:41.500 --> 01:19:42.791
Kwa hivyo ni yako sasa?

01:19:42.875 --> 01:19:44.625
-Kitaalamu, ndiyo. -Kitaalamu?

01:19:45.208 --> 01:19:47.416
-Hakukuambia ilikuwa wapi. -Hapana.

01:19:48.000 --> 01:19:50.208
Akaunti zake ni tupu. Hakuna kitu.

01:19:51.083 --> 01:19:51.958
Kwa hivyo iko wapi?

01:19:52.708 --> 01:19:55.291
Na kisha, niligundua, miaka 50 iliyopita,

01:19:55.375 --> 01:19:59.125
Ni njia gani salama zaidi ya Prentice kuficha dola milioni 80?

01:19:59.708 --> 01:20:02.500
-Akaunti ya benki ya Uswisi. -Aha!

01:20:03.000 --> 01:20:06.416
Na kwa hivyo unachohitaji kufanya ni kupata nambari hiyo ya akaunti.

01:20:07.333 --> 01:20:08.750
Hakuna bahati hapo?

01:20:08.833 --> 01:20:11.583
Lazima iandikwe mahali fulani.

01:20:11.666 --> 01:20:13.916
Martha anawasilisha kila kitu na hakipo hapa.

01:20:14.000 --> 01:20:15.208
Sijui.

01:20:15.791 --> 01:20:18.666
Hapa. Nilidhani inaweza kuwa msimbo kwa sababu aliendelea kusema,

01:20:18.750 --> 01:20:20.541
"Tufaha la Hawa lingerudishwa kwenye mti."

01:20:20.625 --> 01:20:24.208
Hilo lilikuwa jambo la kawaida. Kana kwamba tufaha la Eve ndilo bahati.

01:20:24.291 --> 01:20:26.750
Lakini akaunti ya Uswisi, tunatafuta nambari 19,

01:20:26.833 --> 01:20:28.041
kwa hivyo haifanyi kazi.

01:20:28.583 --> 01:20:30.708
Vera, je, aliwahi kukuambia chochote?

01:20:31.583 --> 01:20:34.708
Hata kama angefanya hivyo, ningeenda kaburini mwangu kabla ya kukupa.

01:20:35.500 --> 01:20:36.583
Ndiyo.

01:20:37.666 --> 01:20:40.916
Ungefanya chochote kumzuia mwana mpotevu asipate utajiri huo.

01:20:41.000 --> 01:20:42.208
Inakuchoma.

01:20:42.916 --> 01:20:44.333
Wewe mjanja mchungu.

01:20:45.375 --> 01:20:46.791
Pesa hizo

01:20:47.375 --> 01:20:52.791
Ni zaburi moja katika Biblia inayoelezea uchungu wangu, wewe mtoto mchafu.

01:20:53.458 --> 01:20:57.541
Unapaswa kuja kuchukua vitu vyako, vitatokea mtaani.

01:21:03.208 --> 01:21:06.625
Wewe. Wewe ni mpelelezi. Nitakulipa. Sijali, hii ni muhimu sana,

01:21:06.708 --> 01:21:09.541
Urithi wangu na taaluma yangu ya kisiasa ya siku zijazo inategemea hilo.

01:21:09.625 --> 01:21:11.750
Je, unaweza kufikiria chochote?

01:21:11.833 --> 01:21:15.250
Je, kuna uhusiano gani na Apple ya Eve ambayo inaweza kuwa na nambari hiyo?

01:21:17.208 --> 01:21:20.291
Loo, um… Mm-mm.

01:21:20.916 --> 01:21:22.750
Lakini ukifikiria chochote, utanipigia simu?

01:21:22.833 --> 01:21:24.833
-Oh, ndio. Unaweka dau. -Sawa.

01:21:32.208 --> 01:21:33.541
Tunapaswa kuangalia kila mahali.

01:21:38.458 --> 01:21:41.541
Huenda ikawa, uh, imeshonwa kwenye bitana.

01:21:42.166 --> 01:21:44.458
Imechongwa kwenye chuma.

01:22:04.875 --> 01:22:06.166
Hii ni tupu.

01:22:06.750 --> 01:22:08.166
Ndiyo. Fanya hivyo.

01:22:29.625 --> 01:22:31.250
Nikumbushe kuwasilisha hili.

01:22:31.333 --> 01:22:32.541
Faili hiyo.

01:22:33.791 --> 01:22:35.750
-Haina maana. -Najua.

01:22:35.833 --> 01:22:37.875
Bahati ya dola milioni 80.

01:22:37.958 --> 01:22:39.708
Lakini kama Apple ya Eve ndiyo bahati

01:22:39.791 --> 01:22:42.875
na si rundo la pesa taslimu katika akaunti ya Uswisi mahali fulani, ni nini?

01:22:47.000 --> 01:22:47.833
Nini?

01:22:47.916 --> 01:22:50.000
Lazima waliandika tarehe vibaya kwenye hili.

01:22:51.083 --> 01:22:54.583
Inasema kitu cha kufungua crypt kiliagizwa Jumatano iliyopita.

01:22:55.250 --> 01:22:56.666
Hilo haliwezi kuwa sahihi.

01:22:58.541 --> 01:23:01.750
Nani angeagiza vifaa vya mazishi kwa ajili ya mtu ambaye hajafa mapema?

01:23:03.125 --> 01:23:06.250
Mtu ambaye alijua kwa uhakika mkubwa siku na saa yake ingefika lini.

01:23:06.333 --> 01:23:07.541
Nipe hilo.

01:23:08.583 --> 01:23:11.375
Loo, hiyo ni maandishi yaliyochapishwa kwa kompyuta. Hiyo si makosa ya uchapishaji. Hiyo ndiyo yote.

01:23:11.458 --> 01:23:13.916
Yeyote aliyepiga simu kwa mpangilio huo, hiyo ndiyo ufunguo.

01:23:14.000 --> 01:23:15.583
Sawa. Ndiyo. Ndiyo.

01:23:19.333 --> 01:23:21.458
Ujenzi wa Magurudumu ya Chuma. Huyu ni Louise.

01:23:21.541 --> 01:23:24.083
Habari, Louise. Ni Baba Jud kutoka Perpetual Fortitude.

01:23:25.250 --> 01:23:27.416
-Loo. Habari. -Habari, Louise.

01:23:27.500 --> 01:23:29.916
Tulikuwa na kipande cha vifaa vyako vya ujenzi hapa leo.

01:23:30.000 --> 01:23:32.583
-Uh, forklift ya kufungua, um… crypt. -Oh, ndio. Najua.

01:23:32.666 --> 01:23:35.041
Si mara nyingi sana tunapata oda ya kufungua crypt.

01:23:35.125 --> 01:23:36.458
Vizuri. Kwa hivyo nahitaji kujua--

01:23:36.541 --> 01:23:38.875
Kwa kweli nilishughulikia agizo hilo. Mimi hufanya usindikaji wote.

01:23:38.958 --> 01:23:40.625
Ndiyo. Ninachohitaji kujua, Louise, ni--

01:23:40.708 --> 01:23:42.708
-Ninaendesha eneo hili na kaka yangu James. -Sawa.

01:23:42.791 --> 01:23:44.916
-Anapokea maagizo lakini mimi huyashughulikia. -Ndiyo. Sawa.

01:23:45.000 --> 01:23:47.000
Kwa hivyo sababu ya kupiga simu, Louise, ni--

01:23:47.083 --> 01:23:49.833
Nimewahi kufika kanisani kwenu, lakini sidhani kama mlikuwepo.

01:23:49.916 --> 01:23:52.916
-Hapana, mimi… Mimi ni mgeni, mgeni hapa. -Hongera.

01:23:53.000 --> 01:23:55.750
-Louise, mimi… lazima niulize… -Hapana, ilikuwa mtu mzee.

01:23:55.833 --> 01:23:58.208
-Baba… Je, yeye… -Monsignor, Monsignor.

01:23:58.291 --> 01:24:00.041
-Baba Monsignor, sawa, sawa… -Louise--

01:24:00.125 --> 01:24:03.625
Alikuwa akihubiri nilipoenda na lazima nikwambie, huyo si mtu mzuri.

01:24:03.708 --> 01:24:06.500
-Lakini samahani kwamba yeye… -Sawa.

01:24:06.583 --> 01:24:09.000
...salamu, nimekufa na, unajua, kwa hasara yenu nyote ...

01:24:09.083 --> 01:24:11.500
Ndiyo, ni msiba mbaya kwa kila mtu, Louise.

01:24:11.583 --> 01:24:14.000
Je, ninaweza… lazima, uh, nikatize.

01:24:14.083 --> 01:24:16.083
-Nina swali. -Ndiyo.

01:24:16.166 --> 01:24:19.541
Uh, agizo la forklift. Nahitaji kujua ni nani aliyeweka agizo.

01:24:19.625 --> 01:24:22.041
-James anapokea maagizo na… -James anapokea maagizo.

01:24:22.125 --> 01:24:24.708
-...amebaki kwa siku nzima. -Naweza kupata namba ya James?

01:24:24.791 --> 01:24:27.416
Hili ni muhimu sana. Tunahitaji kujua ni nani aliyeweka agizo hilo.

01:24:27.500 --> 01:24:30.875
-Hapana, hapana. Sidhani kama naweza kufanya hivyo… -Hapana, ni muhimu sana.

01:24:30.958 --> 01:24:33.083
-Samahani, Baba. -Ni sana--

01:24:33.166 --> 01:24:35.166
Ninachoweza kufanya, kama nilivyokuwa nikisema,

01:24:35.250 --> 01:24:38.125
Je, naweza kukupatia taarifa hiyo kisha nitakupa

01:24:38.208 --> 01:24:39.833
-mlio wa kurudi. -Ndivyo hivyo. Ni vizuri sana.

01:24:39.916 --> 01:24:42.541
Na kama ungeweza kumpigia simu James sasa, ningemshukuru sana.

01:24:42.625 --> 01:24:44.541
-Asante, Louise. -Naye atakupigia simu tena.

01:24:44.625 --> 01:24:46.708
Nitafanya hivyo. Baba, naweza kukuuliza jambo fulani?

01:24:46.791 --> 01:24:49.000
Ndiyo, ni… Ingawa, namaanisha…

01:24:49.583 --> 01:24:51.083
Naam, kama unaweza kuifanya haraka.

01:24:51.166 --> 01:24:54.125
-Hiki ni kipaumbele kwetu hivi sasa. -Labda anaweza kukupigia simu tena na--

01:24:54.208 --> 01:24:56.208
Baba Jud angeweza… Je, unaweza…

01:24:57.708 --> 01:24:58.791
Louise?

01:24:58.875 --> 01:25:00.583
Ee Mungu.

01:25:02.250 --> 01:25:03.333
Louise?

01:25:03.958 --> 01:25:05.958
Utaniombea?

01:25:09.500 --> 01:25:10.416
Uh…

01:25:11.375 --> 01:25:13.000
Ndiyo, bila shaka.

01:25:14.416 --> 01:25:17.250
-Naweza kuuliza kwa nini? -Uh…

01:25:18.708 --> 01:25:20.333
Ni, uh, mama yangu.

01:25:22.666 --> 01:25:23.875
Je, ni mgonjwa?

01:25:24.625 --> 01:25:25.708
Ndiyo.

01:25:25.791 --> 01:25:28.333
Um, yuko katika hospitali ya wagonjwa mahututi.

01:25:29.708 --> 01:25:31.333
Samahani sana, Louise.

01:25:31.416 --> 01:25:33.416
Uh, hatanizungumzia.

01:25:33.500 --> 01:25:35.583
Tulipigana mara ya mwisho tulipozungumza.

01:25:35.666 --> 01:25:41.458
Uh, ana uvimbe kwenye ubongo wake unaomuathiri,

01:25:41.541 --> 01:25:45.083
Na inamfanya aseme mambo mabaya sana,

01:25:45.166 --> 01:25:47.291
na kwa hivyo nilisema mambo mabaya

01:25:47.375 --> 01:25:50.083
na sasa ninaogopa kwamba hilo litakuwa jambo la mwisho

01:25:50.166 --> 01:25:52.166
ambayo huwa tunaambiana.

01:25:54.833 --> 01:25:56.916
Baba, mimi, um…

01:25:58.833 --> 01:26:02.250
Ninahisi upweke sana, um, hivi sasa.

01:26:05.541 --> 01:26:08.750
Samahani sana, Louise.

01:26:10.083 --> 01:26:11.291
Hauko peke yako.

01:26:12.750 --> 01:26:14.166
Niko hapa.

01:26:14.958 --> 01:26:16.166
Niko hapa.

01:26:17.041 --> 01:26:18.541
Unaweza kuniambia jina la mama yako?

01:26:47.458 --> 01:26:50.083
Ninaomba kwamba Barbara aweze kuhisi upendo wa binti yake.

01:26:51.166 --> 01:26:55.000
Kwamba itampa faraja katika wakati huu, na, Bwana, namwombea Louise.

01:26:56.416 --> 01:26:58.625
Kuwa naye na umpe hekima na mwongozo.

01:26:58.708 --> 01:27:02.125
Mshike mikononi mwako mwaminifu na umjulishe kwamba anapendwa.

01:27:02.666 --> 01:27:04.291
Hayuko peke yake.

01:27:04.916 --> 01:27:08.333
Tunaomba haya kupitia Kristo Bwana wetu. Amina.

01:27:09.166 --> 01:27:10.125
Sawa, Louise.

01:27:10.750 --> 01:27:13.416
Una nambari yangu. Wakati wowote, mchana au usiku,

01:27:13.500 --> 01:27:14.791
Niko hapa kwa ajili yako.

01:27:15.291 --> 01:27:17.250
Kanisa hili liko hapa kwa ajili yako.

01:27:17.333 --> 01:27:18.500
Ubarikiwe. Sawa.

01:27:19.041 --> 01:27:22.041
Dhoruba. Nilikuja karibu.

01:27:23.791 --> 01:27:26.416
Nitachukua kanisa. Wewe shughulikia kasisi.

01:27:30.375 --> 01:27:32.625
Usinifuate, Blanc. Nimemaliza.

01:27:32.708 --> 01:27:34.541
Na, uh, kwa nini hasa?

01:27:34.625 --> 01:27:37.083
Nimekuwa na jambo la "njia ya kwenda Damasko".

01:27:37.166 --> 01:27:39.750
Paulo alipata ufunuo mtakatifu akiwa njiani kuelekea Damasko.

01:27:39.833 --> 01:27:42.708
Ndiyo, najua. Alipigwa kipofu na upuuzi wote huo.

01:27:42.791 --> 01:27:44.791
Labda ni kisa cha jicho la waridi tu.

01:27:44.875 --> 01:27:48.375
Lakini hakuwa karibu kutatua mauaji wakati yalipotokea.

01:27:48.458 --> 01:27:50.875
Namaanisha, unafikiri tunafanya nini hapa?

01:27:51.541 --> 01:27:54.958
Unafikiri kwa nini nikawa kasisi? Hakuna upuuzi. Kweli. Kwa nini?

01:27:58.208 --> 01:27:59.416
Ulihisi hatia.

01:28:00.000 --> 01:28:02.000
Kwa ajili ya kujiua. Na kanisa,

01:28:02.083 --> 01:28:04.916
ilikupa mahali pa kujificha na njia iliyo wazi

01:28:05.000 --> 01:28:07.000
kukupa hisia ya msamaha.

01:28:07.625 --> 01:28:10.500
Yule jamaa niliyemuua ulingoni, nilimchukia.

01:28:11.000 --> 01:28:12.833
Nakumbuka, nilijua alikuwa kwenye shida

01:28:12.916 --> 01:28:15.125
na niliendelea na kuendelea hadi nilipohisi amevunjika.

01:28:15.208 --> 01:28:17.833
Haikuwa ajali. Nilimuua kwa chuki moyoni mwangu.

01:28:17.916 --> 01:28:20.250
Hakuna kujificha kutoka kwa hilo, hakuna kulitatua.

01:28:20.333 --> 01:28:24.166
Mungu hakunificha wala kunirekebisha. Ananipenda ninapokuwa na hatia.

01:28:24.250 --> 01:28:26.375
Hilo ndilo ninalopaswa kuwafanyia watu hawa.

01:28:26.458 --> 01:28:27.750
Sio mchezo huu wa whodunit.

01:28:27.833 --> 01:28:29.083
Hapana, sasa subiri kidogo.

01:28:35.375 --> 01:28:37.583
Samahani. Samahani, mimi--

01:28:38.333 --> 01:28:40.166
Ungeniangalia ninapozungumza nawe?

01:28:40.250 --> 01:28:42.250
Tunatafuta muuaji. Huu si mchezo.

01:28:42.333 --> 01:28:43.708
Ni mchezo!

01:28:43.791 --> 01:28:45.416
Kutatua, kushinda.

01:28:45.500 --> 01:28:47.541
Kupata wakati wako mkubwa wa checkmate.

01:28:47.625 --> 01:28:51.458
Na kwa kunitumia ndani yake, unaniweka kinyume na kusudi langu halisi na la pekee maishani.

01:28:51.541 --> 01:28:54.166
Ambayo si kupigana na waovu na kuwafikisha mbele ya haki,

01:28:54.250 --> 01:28:57.458
bali kuwatumikia na kuwaleta kwa Kristo.

01:28:57.541 --> 01:28:59.375
Vinginevyo, mimi ni mbaya kama Wicks.

01:28:59.458 --> 01:29:01.458
Kuifanya iwe juu yangu na si Yesu.

01:29:02.500 --> 01:29:04.916
Sikiliza, huna haja ya kuelewa, Blanc.

01:29:05.000 --> 01:29:06.541
Lakini tafadhali tu,

01:29:06.625 --> 01:29:08.916
tafadhali, tafadhali, tafadhali niache.

01:29:15.625 --> 01:29:17.458
-Je, unaweza kusema hivyo tena? -Hapana.

01:29:17.541 --> 01:29:20.416
Kuhusu kujifanya kukuhusu wewe, si Yesu. Kama Wicks, ulisema.

01:29:20.500 --> 01:29:22.708
Baba, hili ni muhimu.

01:29:22.791 --> 01:29:24.291
Nisaidie kuelewa!

01:29:24.375 --> 01:29:27.375
Tuko hapa kuitumikia dunia, si kuishinda.

01:29:28.125 --> 01:29:30.333
-Hicho ndicho Kristo alifanya. -Kwa hivyo?

01:29:30.416 --> 01:29:33.250
Kwa hivyo Wicks alipokuwa akizungumzia kuhusu kupigana na ulimwengu kwa ajili ya Kristo,

01:29:33.333 --> 01:29:36.791
Hakuwa akizungumzia kuhusu Kristo, alikuwa akizungumzia kuhusu ubinafsi wake mwenyewe.

01:29:36.875 --> 01:29:39.708
Na nguvu. Hakuwahi kuzungumzia kuhusu Kristo.

01:29:41.833 --> 01:29:45.041
Ndiyo, mara kwa mara alizungumzia kuhusu Kristo akifufuka katika nguvu.

01:29:45.125 --> 01:29:47.041
Kulipiza kisasi chake kwa wasio waaminifu.

01:29:47.125 --> 01:29:48.958
Tufaha la Eve ndilo hazina.

01:29:49.041 --> 01:29:51.458
"Tufaha la Hawa limerudishwa kwenye mti."

01:29:51.541 --> 01:29:52.875
Sasa, hiyo ina maana gani?

01:29:52.958 --> 01:29:55.375
Blanc. Sijui.

01:29:56.291 --> 01:29:57.916
Na sijali.

01:30:03.875 --> 01:30:06.625
Huyo atakuwa Geraldine akija kwa ajili ya taarifa mpya kuhusu kesi hiyo.

01:30:06.708 --> 01:30:09.333
Sasa, Baba, uko sahihi.

01:30:09.416 --> 01:30:11.416
Huu ni mchezo wangu, si wako.

01:30:11.500 --> 01:30:14.708
Kwa nini usirudi kwenye kasisi? Mimi nitamshughulikia.

01:30:16.291 --> 01:30:17.500
Asante.

01:30:18.208 --> 01:30:20.333
Hakikisha mlango umefungwa unapoondoka.

01:30:23.750 --> 01:30:25.583
Natumai utamkamata muuaji wako, Blanc.

01:30:26.458 --> 01:30:27.833
Asante. Mimi… nitafanya hivyo.

01:30:45.250 --> 01:30:46.666
Baba Jud?

01:30:47.333 --> 01:30:49.083
-Baba Jud. -Hayupo hapa.

01:30:49.166 --> 01:30:50.166
Njoo.

01:30:50.666 --> 01:30:53.875
Nataka upekue vyumba vya nyuma na vitu hivyo vya kabati pia.

01:30:57.250 --> 01:30:58.083
Loo!

01:30:59.166 --> 01:31:00.583
Ni nzuri, sivyo?

01:31:00.666 --> 01:31:01.958
Nzuri sana, kwa kweli.

01:31:02.041 --> 01:31:04.375
Hasa sehemu ambayo Gideon Fell anakuongoza kupitia

01:31:04.458 --> 01:31:06.375
suluhisho zinazowezekana za uhalifu uliofungwa.

01:31:06.458 --> 01:31:07.416
-Mm. -Ndiyo.

01:31:07.500 --> 01:31:09.666
Ulizungumzia tatu kati yao, kisha ukasimama.

01:31:10.291 --> 01:31:12.500
Sasa, baada ya kusoma ya nne, najua ni kwa nini.

01:31:13.125 --> 01:31:15.208
Tazama, nilitazama tena video hiyo na nikagundua kitu.

01:31:16.416 --> 01:31:18.625
Kuanzia wakati Jud anaingia chumbani,

01:31:19.125 --> 01:31:23.291
hadi wa kwanza wa kundi atakapoona mstari wa kuonekana kwenye kabati hilo

01:31:24.000 --> 01:31:25.416
ni sekunde tisa.

01:31:25.916 --> 01:31:28.750
Sekunde tisa peke yangu na bila kuonekana.

01:31:29.666 --> 01:31:33.500
Muda mwingi wa kufanya tendo hilo kwa kisu kilichofichwa.

01:31:37.166 --> 01:31:39.000
Hivyo ndivyo ilivyofanyika, sivyo?

01:31:39.083 --> 01:31:40.291
Hakuna michezo.

01:31:40.791 --> 01:31:43.416
Hakuna upuuzi. Hivi ndivyo ilivyofanyika.

01:31:45.375 --> 01:31:47.041
Ndiyo.

01:31:48.250 --> 01:31:50.875
Na ulijua. Ulijua tangu mwanzo na ulicheza na mtoto huyo maskini

01:31:50.958 --> 01:31:52.583
-kama paka mwenye panya. -Hapana.

01:31:52.666 --> 01:31:55.166
Sina picha kamili bado.

01:31:55.250 --> 01:31:57.500
-Kama ungeweza kunipa muda zaidi kidogo... -Hapana.

01:31:57.583 --> 01:31:59.875
-Nitaweza kupata-- -Hapana!

01:31:59.958 --> 01:32:02.375
Nimempata muuaji wangu na ninamleta ndani.

01:32:03.208 --> 01:32:04.416
Yuko wapi?

01:33:40.583 --> 01:33:41.500
Peke yangu!

01:34:58.291 --> 01:34:59.500
Nani yuko hapo?

01:35:04.833 --> 01:35:06.041
Subiri!

01:35:13.625 --> 01:35:14.708
Blanc?

01:35:14.791 --> 01:35:15.875
Hapa.

01:35:16.541 --> 01:35:19.458
Loo, shetani. Ni nani huyo?

01:35:19.541 --> 01:35:21.375
Mtunza shamba, Samson.

01:35:22.875 --> 01:35:24.708
Nini kimetokea?

01:35:39.125 --> 01:35:40.250
Loo…

01:35:41.208 --> 01:35:43.708
Mm.

01:35:44.958 --> 01:35:45.791
Uh…

01:35:49.625 --> 01:35:51.583
Mm. Ndiyo.

01:35:51.666 --> 01:35:52.666
Sawa.

01:35:53.208 --> 01:35:56.625
Sawa, Wicks alikuwa amekufa 100% kiafya.

01:35:56.708 --> 01:35:59.125
Namaanisha, tunajua hili, mimi ni…

01:35:59.625 --> 01:36:01.041
kusema tu, sivyo?

01:36:02.333 --> 01:36:03.416
Sawa.

01:36:05.666 --> 01:36:08.875
Sawa, basi naweza pia kusema kwa sauti kubwa,

01:36:09.458 --> 01:36:11.875
Mwanadamu hawezi kufufuka tu kutoka kwa wafu.

01:36:11.958 --> 01:36:14.791
Namaanisha, ni wazi kuna mambo ya ajabu ya Scooby-Doo yanayoendelea hapa.

01:36:15.291 --> 01:36:16.708
"Scooby-Dooby-Doo."

01:36:16.791 --> 01:36:20.625
Sifa kwa Mungu! Sifa na utukufu kwa Mwenyezi!

01:36:20.708 --> 01:36:22.125
Msifuni!

01:36:22.208 --> 01:36:26.125
Sifa na utukufu kwa Mwenyezi Mungu! Sifa na utukufu kwa Mwenyezi.

01:36:26.208 --> 01:36:29.000
-Amemlea Mwanawe. -Haya, Ritz.

01:36:29.083 --> 01:36:30.500
Weka mzunguko barabarani.

01:36:30.583 --> 01:36:33.000
Habari zitaenea haraka na sitaki vituko vyovyote.

01:36:33.083 --> 01:36:34.500
-Umeelewa. -Mkuu!

01:36:34.583 --> 01:36:35.416
Nini?

01:36:35.500 --> 01:36:37.625
Taa hiyo ya kigunduzi cha mwendo pale, pia ni kamera.

01:36:37.708 --> 01:36:39.958
Lakini haijaunganishwa na chochote.

01:36:40.041 --> 01:36:41.166
Kamera, sivyo?

01:36:41.250 --> 01:36:43.750
Sijui. Labda inarekodi kitu kwenye chipu ndani.

01:36:43.833 --> 01:36:45.958
Kwa nini usiilete kwenye maabara ya vyombo vya habari?

01:36:46.625 --> 01:36:48.208
Haleluya, Mungu asifiwe.

01:36:48.291 --> 01:36:50.708
Amemfufua mtumishi wake kutoka kwa wafu.

01:36:50.791 --> 01:36:53.416
Hujambo, nisaidie? Toa sehemu hii yote, hadi kwenye kichaka.

01:36:53.500 --> 01:36:54.916
-Nimeelewa. -Ni tukio la mauaji.

01:36:55.000 --> 01:36:56.791
Mtunza bustani amekufa.

01:37:08.958 --> 01:37:10.750
Hapana! Tafadhali!

01:37:11.791 --> 01:37:14.208
-Loo, shetani. -Hapana! Hapana, hapana, hapana!

01:37:14.291 --> 01:37:15.708
Je, ninaweza kupata msaada?

01:37:15.791 --> 01:37:17.791
-Tafuta msaada! Martha. -Hapana! Loo, hapana, hapana!

01:37:17.875 --> 01:37:20.083
-Martha, unahitaji kurudi nyuma. -Hapana!

01:37:20.166 --> 01:37:22.541
Martha…

01:37:22.625 --> 01:37:25.666
Kimbia gizani, wewe muuaji!

01:37:27.708 --> 01:37:29.333
Lakini amerudi!

01:37:29.833 --> 01:37:33.541
Na analeta kisasi! Analeta kifo!

01:37:50.750 --> 01:37:52.166
Huyu ni Baba Jud.

01:37:52.250 --> 01:37:54.666
Ah, Baba Jud, ni Louise. Unaendeleaje?

01:37:56.000 --> 01:37:57.291
Uh…

01:37:58.666 --> 01:38:00.291
Ndiyo… Habari, Louise.

01:38:00.791 --> 01:38:03.208
Mimi… Natumai hujachelewa, lakini ulisema ilikuwa ya dharura,

01:38:03.291 --> 01:38:04.916
kwa hivyo nilitaka tu kukuambia…

01:38:05.000 --> 01:38:07.625
Nilizungumza na James na agizo la kuinua forklift

01:38:07.708 --> 01:38:10.333
iliwekwa na Monsignor Wicks.

01:38:11.208 --> 01:38:15.291
Alizungumza na James moja kwa moja kuhusu hilo, kwa hivyo natumaini kwamba hili litafafanua mambo.

01:38:15.916 --> 01:38:19.333
Mungu akubariki, Baba, na uwe na usiku mwema, sawa?

01:38:19.416 --> 01:38:22.000
Uh… Ndiyo.

01:38:22.666 --> 01:38:25.416
Naam, wewe pia, Louise.

01:38:50.916 --> 01:38:52.125
Jeez.

01:38:53.916 --> 01:38:55.000
Ndiyo?

01:38:56.125 --> 01:38:57.958
Punguza mwendo, Martha. Nini?

01:39:00.750 --> 01:39:02.666
Nini?

01:39:02.750 --> 01:39:04.583
-Ni muujiza. -Upuuzi.

01:39:04.666 --> 01:39:07.083
Hapana, ilitokea. Martha alisema kaburi ni tupu.

01:39:07.166 --> 01:39:09.375
Ninawapigia simu kila mtu. Niko njiani sasa.

01:39:15.291 --> 01:39:16.500
Je, wewe, uh…

01:39:17.041 --> 01:39:19.041
Unafanya nini? Huvuti sigara.

01:39:19.125 --> 01:39:20.333
Nilifanya hivyo.

01:39:21.166 --> 01:39:23.000
Nilivuta sigara kwa miaka 15.

01:39:23.083 --> 01:39:25.000
Je, Lee alikupigia simu? Je, alikuambia?

01:39:25.500 --> 01:39:26.708
Ndiyo.

01:39:27.958 --> 01:39:30.250
Sawa. Naam, nitaenda kushuhudia muujiza.

01:39:30.333 --> 01:39:33.416
Unafurahia sigara yako ndani ya nyumba.

01:40:05.083 --> 01:40:06.291
Sifa ziwe juu.

01:40:07.416 --> 01:40:08.833
Imetimizwa.

01:40:10.833 --> 01:40:13.875
Njoo.

01:40:15.791 --> 01:40:17.500
Haya, ni…

01:40:18.333 --> 01:40:19.541
Ameipata.

01:40:23.041 --> 01:40:26.125
Sawa, kwa hivyo… si ubora mzuri…

01:40:26.208 --> 01:40:27.625
-Ni sawa. -…lakini, uh…

01:40:38.458 --> 01:40:39.875
Ninaangalia nini hapa?

01:40:46.833 --> 01:40:47.833
Sawa.

01:40:47.916 --> 01:40:51.375
Um, ndio, kwa hivyo, inarekodi wakati wowote kuna mwendo

01:40:51.458 --> 01:40:54.875
na kipande hiki ni sekunde nne baadaye.

01:41:07.041 --> 01:41:09.000
Sawa?

01:41:09.083 --> 01:41:11.000
Chapisho kutoka kwa zana ya bustani.

01:41:12.291 --> 01:41:15.958
Hatukufanya ukaguzi kamili wa hifadhidata, ila tu washukiwa uliowahoji.

01:41:16.666 --> 01:41:17.875
Ni Baba Jud.

01:41:22.750 --> 01:41:23.958
Yuko wapi?

01:41:24.583 --> 01:41:26.416
Laiti ningejua kwa dhati.

01:41:46.041 --> 01:41:47.875
Nyeupe. Nyeupe!

01:41:48.500 --> 01:41:51.125
Nitafanya hivyo. Nita…jigeuza mwenyewe--

01:41:51.208 --> 01:41:53.208
-…388. -388, njiani.

01:41:53.791 --> 01:41:54.791
433.

