-Ninajisalimisha. -Hapana, wewe sivyo.

01:41:57.708 --> 01:42:02.000
Skimbleshanks, paka wa reli!

01:42:03.166 --> 01:42:05.916
Nilifanya hivyo. Nilimuua Samsoni. Nina hatia. Lazima nikiri.

01:42:06.000 --> 01:42:07.083
-Niachie nje. -Sikiliza.

01:42:07.166 --> 01:42:09.583
Utaniambia haswa kilichotokea, lakini hivi sasa,

01:42:09.666 --> 01:42:11.291
Ninawezaje kufika nyumbani kwa Dkt. Nat?

01:42:11.375 --> 01:42:12.875
-Dk. Nat? -Ndiyo, haraka.

01:42:13.375 --> 01:42:14.583
Najuta kuchelewa kwangu.

01:42:14.666 --> 01:42:17.000
Natumai tu hatujachelewa sana. Sasa, shuka tu!

01:42:21.416 --> 01:42:23.541
Salamu Maria, umejaa neema, Bwana yu pamoja nawe.

01:42:23.625 --> 01:42:25.041
Umebarikiwa miongoni mwa wanawake...

01:42:25.125 --> 01:42:27.291
...bwana, kwamba nakuheshimu. Ninaheshimu beji.

01:42:27.375 --> 01:42:30.583
Lakini hili ni kanisa letu na sikwambii kwamba nitatumia vurugu,

01:42:30.666 --> 01:42:34.416
lakini tutakaa hapa usiku kucha ikitubidi. Tunaona mtaro huo!

01:42:34.500 --> 01:42:36.500
-Je, ni kweli? -Hawaturuhusu kuingia.

01:42:36.583 --> 01:42:39.166
Nahitaji kuona.

01:42:39.875 --> 01:42:41.791
Tafadhali, nahitaji kuona.

01:42:59.541 --> 01:43:00.750
Usiku wa Dk.?

01:43:35.625 --> 01:43:37.833
Ee Mungu.

01:43:38.583 --> 01:43:40.000
Harufu hiyo ni nini?

01:43:45.375 --> 01:43:47.000
Subiri tu hapa.

01:43:49.041 --> 01:43:50.125
Blanc.

01:43:50.666 --> 01:43:51.750
Ndiyo.

01:43:56.708 --> 01:43:58.125
Ee Mungu.

01:44:11.333 --> 01:44:12.416
Sawa.

01:44:14.083 --> 01:44:18.750
Ee Bwana, hiyo ni…

01:44:30.166 --> 01:44:31.250
Vijiti.

01:44:31.333 --> 01:44:33.500
Ndiyo, huyo ni… Ni yeye.

01:44:34.375 --> 01:44:35.791
-Je, yeye… -Ndiyo.

01:44:36.500 --> 01:44:39.958
Namaanisha, kwa kile kinachostahili siku hizi.

01:44:42.583 --> 01:44:44.708
Hebu tuone sasa. Hebu…

01:44:48.000 --> 01:44:49.250
Sawa.

01:44:50.750 --> 01:44:53.083
Hili linaweza kuwa jambo lisilopendeza.

01:44:53.166 --> 01:44:54.791
Namaanisha, ni jambo lisilopendeza zaidi.

01:45:30.333 --> 01:45:31.416
Dkt. Nat.

01:45:32.666 --> 01:45:35.500
Katika mwili. Ndiyo… Au, ni nini kilichobaki.

01:46:08.500 --> 01:46:10.500
Geraldine, ni… ni Blanc. Um…

01:46:11.625 --> 01:46:13.791
Naam, amesimama hapa.

01:46:13.875 --> 01:46:15.375
Nisikilize.

01:46:15.458 --> 01:46:17.625
Utataka kuja nyumbani kwa Dkt. Nat.

01:46:17.708 --> 01:46:21.125
Kuna mwili. Au miwili.

01:46:22.250 --> 01:46:23.666
Yote yako hapa.

01:46:24.166 --> 01:46:27.041
Ndiyo, ndiyo. Ni…imekwisha, ndiyo.

01:46:28.166 --> 01:46:29.666
Nitakupigia simu tena.

01:46:30.958 --> 01:46:32.791
Baba Jud. Subiri, subiri.

01:46:32.875 --> 01:46:35.000
Nilimuua Samsoni. Lazima nifanye hivi.

01:46:35.625 --> 01:46:38.250
Lazima nifanye hivyo kwa hiari yangu mwenyewe la sivyo haitakuwa na maana yoyote.

01:46:53.791 --> 01:46:57.916
Angalia kwenye bamba. Nakili hiyo. Vitengo vyovyote vinavyopatikana vya kujibu…

01:46:58.000 --> 01:47:00.125
Ungependa kunipigia simu Geraldine, tafadhali?

01:47:00.625 --> 01:47:03.458
Sema Padre Jud amerudi kanisani kwake na yuko tayari kukiri.

01:47:20.041 --> 01:47:22.750
Baba Jud. Niko hapa kukukamata kwa mauaji hayo

01:47:22.833 --> 01:47:25.083
ya Monsinyori Jefferson Wicks na Samson Holt.

01:47:25.166 --> 01:47:29.333
Na wewe ni mtu anayependezwa na kifo cha Dkt. Nathaniel Sharp.

01:47:29.416 --> 01:47:30.833
Nat amekufa?

01:47:32.041 --> 01:47:33.333
Aliuawa nyumbani kwake.

01:47:34.333 --> 01:47:36.833
Pia tuliupata mwili wa Wicks. Umekwisha.

01:47:37.333 --> 01:47:40.458
Chochote unachosema kinaweza kutumika dhidi yako mahakamani.

01:47:40.541 --> 01:47:43.166
Lakini kama ungependa kukiri chochote,

01:47:43.250 --> 01:47:46.083
Hii inaonekana kama mahali pazuri pa kufanyia kazi.

01:47:48.250 --> 01:47:49.333
Ndiyo.

01:47:52.375 --> 01:47:54.125
Miaka iliyopita,

01:47:54.208 --> 01:47:56.625
Nilimuua mtu kwenye ulingo wa ndondi.

01:47:58.333 --> 01:48:00.375
Nilimuua kwa chuki moyoni mwangu.

01:48:02.500 --> 01:48:05.916
Jana usiku, dhambi hiyo hiyo ilinijia na katika muda mfupi wa

01:48:06.875 --> 01:48:09.041
hofu na hasira, mimi--

01:48:13.500 --> 01:48:17.541
Samahani, hilo lilikuwa jambo la kushtua, lakini nilihitaji uache kuongea.

01:48:17.625 --> 01:48:19.875
-Hapana. Baba Jud-- -Nilikuwa karibu kuwaelezea kila mtu…

01:48:19.958 --> 01:48:21.708
-Kaa chini na usikilize. -Acha kuongea.

01:48:21.791 --> 01:48:24.750
Tafadhali, mwache. Ulikuwa unaendelea… Endelea, ulisema jana usiku…

01:48:24.833 --> 01:48:27.166
-Katika wakati wa hofu na ghadhabu... -Nilikuwa karibu kufanya hivyo...

01:48:27.250 --> 01:48:30.333
Hutanyamazisha sauti ya Bwana!

01:48:30.416 --> 01:48:35.333
Lakini kaa sasa uone uovu na aibu ya wenye hatia

01:48:35.416 --> 01:48:38.250
kuwekwa wazi mbele yenu nyote!

01:48:51.000 --> 01:48:54.125
Unafanya nini?

01:48:57.208 --> 01:49:00.416
Tuanze na mauaji ya Wicks.

01:49:00.500 --> 01:49:03.333
Hapa hapa Ijumaa Kuu.

01:49:04.041 --> 01:49:05.875
Uhalifu usiowezekana.

01:49:07.250 --> 01:49:09.875
Na, Geraldine, ulikuwa sahihi katika hitimisho lako.

01:49:09.958 --> 01:49:14.125
Monsignor Wicks alipoanguka katika chumba hicho cha kabati, hakuwa amekufa.

01:49:14.208 --> 01:49:16.333
Hata hakuwa amedungwa kisu, bado.

01:49:17.333 --> 01:49:20.750
Chupa aliyoiweka kwenye sanduku la kuvunja

01:49:20.833 --> 01:49:24.541
ilitiwa dawa ya kutuliza yenye nguvu sana.

01:49:24.625 --> 01:49:26.416
Alikunywa kutoka humo.

01:49:26.500 --> 01:49:28.375
Alijiimarisha.

01:49:28.458 --> 01:49:31.666
Na ndani ya dakika chache, akaanguka sakafuni, bila fahamu.

01:49:31.750 --> 01:49:34.708
Kiburi kizito.

01:49:34.791 --> 01:49:36.625
Kumwacha hana kinga

01:49:36.708 --> 01:49:40.125
na kumpa muuaji nafasi yake ya kuingia chumbani

01:49:40.708 --> 01:49:42.375
na kutoa pigo la kufisha.

01:49:43.000 --> 01:49:44.208
Mimi… tayari nimesema hivyo.

01:49:44.791 --> 01:49:45.625
Baba Jud.

01:49:45.708 --> 01:49:48.541
Hapana. Kisu kilikuwa mgongoni mwake nilipompata.

01:49:48.625 --> 01:49:50.208
Kuna kitu mgongoni mwake.

01:49:50.291 --> 01:49:53.333
Kwa hivyo vipi? Lini? Haiwezekani. Niliona.

01:49:53.416 --> 01:49:54.875
Uliona nini?

01:49:56.083 --> 01:49:57.500
Kichwa cha shetani chekundu.

01:49:57.583 --> 01:50:00.791
Damu uliyodhani ilikuwa ya Wicks.

01:50:00.875 --> 01:50:03.125
Sasa, nimekuonyesha jibu la hili, umeona?

01:50:04.375 --> 01:50:05.666
Ibilisi.

01:50:05.750 --> 01:50:07.333
Baa ya pizza. Picha.

01:50:08.666 --> 01:50:10.666
Ulidhani umeona,

01:50:11.208 --> 01:50:13.125
lakini haikuwa hivyo, hapana.

01:50:13.208 --> 01:50:15.416
Ilikuwa taa ya pili inayofanana.

01:50:15.500 --> 01:50:18.375
Kichwa cha pili cha shetani kinachofanana.

01:50:19.708 --> 01:50:20.791
Ndiyo.

01:50:23.791 --> 01:50:25.416
Na pia ilikuwa haipo.

01:50:26.041 --> 01:50:27.458
Mashetani wawili.

01:50:27.541 --> 01:50:28.875
Ndiyo.

01:50:28.958 --> 01:50:30.166
Kwa nini mbili?

01:50:31.041 --> 01:50:32.666
Na kwa nini rangi nyekundu?

01:50:32.750 --> 01:50:34.166
Haikuwa nyekundu hata hivyo. Sasa ni nyekundu.

01:50:34.250 --> 01:50:37.000
Nyekundu sawa na vazi la Ijumaa Kuu.

01:50:37.083 --> 01:50:38.916
Nyekundu sawa kabisa

01:50:39.000 --> 01:50:42.083
kama uzi wa ajabu uliopatikana kabatini.

01:50:42.791 --> 01:50:46.583
Kwa sababu kichwa cha pili cha shetani kilikuwepo wakati wote.

01:50:46.666 --> 01:50:49.000
Ameshonwa nyuma ya mavazi yake.

01:50:49.083 --> 01:50:50.375
Tupu, nyepesi,

01:50:50.458 --> 01:50:52.541
na kujazwa na chembe ndogo ya damu

01:50:53.125 --> 01:50:56.041
Imesababishwa na kidhibiti cha mbali cha RF.

01:50:57.000 --> 01:51:00.208
Anza safari kwa wakati unaofaa kabisa.

01:51:00.291 --> 01:51:01.125
Monsignor?

01:51:02.500 --> 01:51:03.375
Daktari.

01:51:05.125 --> 01:51:06.416
Sauti ya mamlaka

01:51:06.500 --> 01:51:10.041
ambaye anaweza kusubiri ugunduzi anaohitaji kabla ya kuchukua jukumu.

01:51:10.125 --> 01:51:11.333
Kuna kitu mgongoni mwake.

01:51:11.416 --> 01:51:13.041
Subiri. Usiguse.

01:51:15.333 --> 01:51:17.750
Wakati wa kukengeushwa unajitokeza.

01:51:20.333 --> 01:51:22.333
Na tendo hilo linafanywa haraka.

01:51:23.833 --> 01:51:25.083
Kazi yake ya mwisho,

01:51:25.166 --> 01:51:29.500
kuondoa chupa iliyofungwa dawa za kulevya inayosababisha hatia.

01:51:29.583 --> 01:51:32.416
Lakini ilikuwa wapi? Ilikuwa imetoweka.

01:51:33.541 --> 01:51:35.750
Kikwazo kimoja katika mpango wake.

01:51:35.833 --> 01:51:39.708
Matokeo ya wakati wa neema ya kipumbavu kutoka kwa Padre Jud

01:51:40.291 --> 01:51:44.833
ambaye alificha chupa ili kuficha unywaji wa Wicks

01:51:44.916 --> 01:51:47.750
na akarudi baadaye ili kuichukua.

01:51:50.083 --> 01:51:51.291
Mungu wangu.

01:51:51.791 --> 01:51:52.958
Nat.

01:51:53.041 --> 01:51:54.250
Kwa nini?

01:51:54.750 --> 01:51:57.000
Wicks alikuwa anaenda kuunguza dunia.

01:51:57.083 --> 01:51:58.708
Alikuwa anaenda kumharibu.

01:51:58.791 --> 01:52:01.625
Hapana. Sababu kubwa zaidi. Sababu iliyokuleta hapa.

01:52:01.708 --> 01:52:04.125
Kwa nini unafanya mambo haya yote ya kichaa na ya kina?

01:52:04.208 --> 01:52:07.083
Uhalifu usiowezekana.

01:52:07.166 --> 01:52:08.375
Kwa nini?

01:52:09.041 --> 01:52:10.250
Hakika.

01:52:10.333 --> 01:52:12.833
Sawa, kwa hivyo ... ikiwa Dkt. Nat angemuua Wicks,

01:52:13.375 --> 01:52:14.375
Nani alimuua Nat?

01:52:14.458 --> 01:52:16.291
Naam, sasa tunafikia.

01:52:17.000 --> 01:52:19.750
Sio fumbo la mlango uliofungwa kwa nguvu

01:52:19.833 --> 01:52:23.208
na vifaa na vidokezo,

01:52:23.291 --> 01:52:26.708
lakini mpango mkubwa zaidi.

01:52:26.791 --> 01:52:31.875
Mtu ambaye mizizi yake inaelekea kwenye msingi wa kanisa hili.

01:52:31.958 --> 01:52:33.708
Na moja linalonivutia,

01:52:33.791 --> 01:52:37.041
asiyeamini kwa kila maana ya neno,

01:52:37.125 --> 01:52:40.041
katika ulimwengu wa imani.

01:52:41.666 --> 01:52:43.500
Ili kuelewa kesi hii,

01:52:44.541 --> 01:52:48.625
Ilinibidi niangalie hadithi ya uwongo iliyokuwa ikijengwa.

01:52:48.708 --> 01:52:51.541
Sio kutatua kama ilikuwa kweli au la,

01:52:51.625 --> 01:52:54.041
lakini kuhisi katika nafsi yangu

01:52:54.125 --> 01:52:57.250
kiini cha kile ambacho ilijitahidi kuwasilisha.

01:53:00.541 --> 01:53:01.958
Kuhani mtakatifu.

01:53:02.708 --> 01:53:08.125
Hakupigwa na mtu yeyote, ila kwa mkono wa Shetani mwenyewe.

01:53:08.208 --> 01:53:11.625
Alizikwa katika kaburi la baba yake lililofungwa,

01:53:12.208 --> 01:53:13.625
lakini kisha akainuka

01:53:14.333 --> 01:53:15.958
kwa mapenzi ya Mungu.

01:53:16.041 --> 01:53:18.041
Imefufuka kama kitu kipya.

01:53:18.125 --> 01:53:20.125
Si mtu wa kukosea tena,

01:53:20.208 --> 01:53:24.041
lakini sasa ni ishara ya nguvu ya Bwana juu ya kifo.

01:53:26.000 --> 01:53:27.625
Haki yake kwa watakatifu.

01:53:28.125 --> 01:53:30.375
Kisasi chake kwa waovu.

01:53:33.166 --> 01:53:37.000
Sawa. Na sasa, nini hasa kilitokea?

01:53:37.083 --> 01:53:39.083
Ndiyo. Ndiyo.

01:53:39.166 --> 01:53:43.000
Ni wakati wa kuvunja uso huu mchafu

01:53:43.083 --> 01:53:47.083
ya miujiza na ufufuo na kufichua kile kilichotokea kweli.

01:53:47.166 --> 01:53:49.583
Ni wakati wa Benoit Blanc's

01:53:49.666 --> 01:53:52.750
mchunguzi wa mwisho kuhusu mafumbo ya imani!

01:54:21.291 --> 01:54:23.291
Blanc, uko sawa… Uko sawa?

01:54:25.416 --> 01:54:26.625
Damasko.

01:54:27.666 --> 01:54:28.875
Damasko?

01:54:30.250 --> 01:54:33.291
Kama ... kitu cha barabara kwenda Damasko?

01:54:33.375 --> 01:54:35.250
Ndiyo, ndiyo, Damasko.

01:54:38.791 --> 01:54:40.416
Shit.

01:54:41.291 --> 01:54:42.375
Blanc?

01:54:58.916 --> 01:55:00.541
Siwezi kutatua kesi hii.

01:55:04.500 --> 01:55:05.500
Nini?

01:55:06.583 --> 01:55:09.375
Unasema hivyo kwa hitimisho lako, Benoit Blanc,

01:55:09.458 --> 01:55:12.416
Je, huyo Monsignor Wicks alifufuka kutoka kwa wafu?

01:55:12.500 --> 01:55:13.916
Kwamba ilikuwa muujiza?

01:55:14.000 --> 01:55:18.125
Ninasema siwezi kutatua kesi hii.

01:55:19.666 --> 01:55:20.750
Hilo linafanya kazi.

01:55:21.250 --> 01:55:22.083
Asante.

01:55:24.458 --> 01:55:25.541
Blanc?

01:55:26.250 --> 01:55:28.666
Ukijua kilichotokea kweli, unapaswa kuwaambia kila mtu.

01:55:28.750 --> 01:55:32.458
Je, huku ndiko kutunza imani yetu au kuwa na heshima au kitu kama hicho?

01:55:32.541 --> 01:55:34.750
Kwa sababu tunastahili ukweli.

01:55:34.833 --> 01:55:36.250
Sio hivyo.

01:55:37.625 --> 01:55:39.250
Ninahitaji ukweli.

01:55:40.541 --> 01:55:42.833
Huwezi tu

01:55:42.916 --> 01:55:45.791
Tupe jibu? Je, si ndiyo maana ya haya yote?

01:55:48.583 --> 01:55:51.541
Na ungependa kufikiria kuibadilisha kitabu changu kuwa cha kuficha?

01:55:51.625 --> 01:55:53.333
Hapana.

01:55:53.958 --> 01:55:56.500
Sawa. Sawa. Onyesho limekwisha. Kila mtu yuko nje.

01:55:57.333 --> 01:55:59.750
Nje. Nje.

01:56:00.458 --> 01:56:02.166
Naam, unaweza kusimama nyuma, bwana?

01:56:03.458 --> 01:56:05.083
Sawa, tunaweza kuwazuia…

01:56:06.750 --> 01:56:09.583
Ninaongeza sura nyingine kisha tuko… tuko tayari.

01:56:09.666 --> 01:56:12.000
Tuko tayari kuchapisha. Niamini, Alan.

01:56:12.083 --> 01:56:14.708
Piga simu Random House, kila mtu. Itakuwa kubwa!

01:56:17.833 --> 01:56:21.708
Kile ambacho tumeshuhudia ni muujiza uliothibitishwa na Benoit Blanc mwenyewe.

01:56:21.791 --> 01:56:25.125
Dunia itajua kilichotokea leo hapa Chimney Rock.

01:56:25.208 --> 01:56:29.208
Unaweza kujijua. Fuata chaneli yangu ya YouTube @CyDraven…

01:56:29.291 --> 01:56:30.500
Ni fujo iliyoje!

01:56:32.000 --> 01:56:34.416
Nadhani watamkamata Padre Jud sasa.

01:56:35.000 --> 01:56:36.083
Ndiyo.

01:56:37.041 --> 01:56:38.666
Nadhani watafanya hivyo.

01:56:44.833 --> 01:56:46.333
Ilikuwa nini hiyo?

01:56:46.875 --> 01:56:48.875
Barabara ya kwenda Damasko.

01:56:49.583 --> 01:56:52.000
Magamba yalianguka kutoka machoni mwangu.

01:56:52.083 --> 01:56:53.916
Kwa hivyo nini? Ukweli, mambo ya kutatanisha?

01:56:54.000 --> 01:56:56.541
Unaamini katika Mungu na mambo haya yote mabaya ni ya kweli?

01:56:56.625 --> 01:56:58.458
Hapana, hapana. Mungu ni hadithi ya kubuni.

01:56:58.541 --> 01:57:00.541
Ufunuo wangu ulitoka…

01:57:01.625 --> 01:57:03.041
kutoka kwa Baba Jud.

01:57:04.500 --> 01:57:06.916
Mfano wake wa kuwa na neema.

01:57:09.583 --> 01:57:11.416
